var book = {
	"name": "Proverbs",
	"numChapters": 31,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16402A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16402A\"></sup>The proverbs of Solomon, son of David, king of Israel:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To know wisdom and instruction,to understand words of insight,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>to receive instruction in wise dealing,in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16404B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16404B\"></sup>righteousness, justice, and equity;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>to give prudence to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16405C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16405C\"></sup>the simple,knowledge and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16405D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16405D\"></sup>discretion to the youth—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Let the wise hear and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16406E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16406E\"></sup>increase in learning,and the one who understands obtain guidance,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>to understand a proverb and a saying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16407F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16407F\"></sup>the words of the wise and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16407G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16407G\"></sup>riddles.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16408H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16408H\"></sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the beginning of knowledge;fools despise wisdom and instruction.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16409I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16409I\"></sup>Hear, my son, your father's instruction,and forsake not your mother's teaching,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>for they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16410J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16410J\"></sup>a graceful garland for your headand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16410K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16410K\"></sup>pendants for your neck.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>My son, if sinners <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16411L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16411L\"></sup>entice you,do not consent.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If they say, “Come with us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16412M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16412M\"></sup>let us lie in wait for blood;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16412N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16412N\"></sup>let us ambush the innocent without reason;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>like Sheol let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16413O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16413O\"></sup>swallow them alive,and whole, like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16413P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16413P\"></sup>those who go down to the pit;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>we shall find all precious goods,we shall fill our houses with plunder;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>throw in your lot among us;we will all have one purse”—",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>my son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16416Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16416Q\"></sup>do not walk in the way with them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16416R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16416R\"></sup>hold back your foot from their paths,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16417S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16417S\"></sup>their feet run to evil,and they make haste to shed blood.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16418T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16418T\"></sup>For in vain is a net spreadin the sight of any bird,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>but these men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16419U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16419U\"></sup>lie in wait for their own blood;they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16419V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16419V\"></sup>set an ambush for their own lives.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16420W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16420W\"></sup>Such are the ways of everyone who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16420X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16420X\"></sup>greedy for unjust gain;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16420Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16420Y\"></sup>it takes away the life of its possessors.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16421Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16421Z\"></sup>Wisdom cries aloud in the street,in the markets she raises her voice;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>at the head of the noisy streets she cries out;at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16422AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16422AA\"></sup>the entrance of the city gates she speaks:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“How long, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16423AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16423AB\"></sup>simple ones, will you love being simple?How long will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16423AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16423AC\"></sup>scoffers delight in their scoffingand fools <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16423AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16423AD\"></sup>hate knowledge?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>If you turn at my reproof,behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16424AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16424AE\"></sup>pour out my spirit to you;I will make my words known to you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16425AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16425AF\"></sup>Because I have called and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16425AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16425AG\"></sup>you refused to listen,have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16425AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16425AH\"></sup>stretched out my hand and no one has heeded,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>because you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16426AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16426AI\"></sup>ignored all my counseland <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16426AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16426AJ\"></sup>would have none of my reproof,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16427AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16427AK\"></sup>will laugh at your calamity;I will mock when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16427AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16427AL\"></sup>terror strikes you,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>when terror strikes you like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16428AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16428AM\"></sup>a stormand your calamity comes like a whirlwind,when distress and anguish come upon you.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16429AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16429AN\"></sup>Then they will call upon me, but I will not answer;they will seek me diligently but will not find me.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Because they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16430AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16430AO\"></sup>hated knowledgeand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16430AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16430AP\"></sup>did not choose the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16431AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16431AQ\"></sup>would have none of my counseland <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16431AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16431AR\"></sup>despised all my reproof,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>therefore they shall eat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16432AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16432AS\"></sup>the fruit of their way,and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16432AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16432AT\"></sup>their fill of their own devices.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For the simple are killed by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16433AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16433AU\"></sup>their turning away,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16433AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16433AV\"></sup>the complacency of fools destroys them;",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16434AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16434AW\"></sup>whoever listens to me will dwell secureand will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16434AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16434AX\"></sup>at ease, without dread of disaster.”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16435A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16435A\"></sup>My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16435B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16435B\"></sup>if you receive my wordsand treasure up my commandments with you,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>making your ear attentive to wisdomand inclining your heart to understanding;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>yes, if you call out for insightand raise your voice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16437C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16437C\"></sup>for understanding,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>if you seek it like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16438D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16438D\"></sup>silverand search for it as for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16438E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16438E\"></sup>hidden treasures,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16439F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16439F\"></sup>you will understand the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and find the knowledge of God.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16440G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16440G\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gives wisdom;from his mouth come knowledge and understanding;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>he stores up sound wisdom for the upright;he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16441H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16441H\"></sup>a shield to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16441I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16441I\"></sup>walk in integrity,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>guarding the paths of justiceand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16442J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16442J\"></sup>watching over the way of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16442K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16442K\"></sup>saints.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16443L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16443L\"></sup>Then you will understand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16443M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16443M\"></sup>righteousness and justiceand equity, every good path;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for wisdom will come into your heart,and knowledge will be pleasant to your soul;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16445N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16445N\"></sup>discretion will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16445O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16445O\"></sup>watch over you,understanding will guard you,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>delivering you from the way of evil,from men of perverted speech,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>who forsake the paths of uprightnessto <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16447P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16447P\"></sup>walk in the ways of darkness,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16448Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16448Q\"></sup>rejoice in doing eviland <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16448R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16448R\"></sup>delight in the perverseness of evil,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>men whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16449S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16449S\"></sup>paths are crooked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16449T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16449T\"></sup>and who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16449U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16449U\"></sup>devious in their ways.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16450V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16450V\"></sup>you will be delivered from the forbidden woman,from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16450W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16450W\"></sup>the adulteress with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16450X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16450X\"></sup>her smooth words,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>who forsakes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16451Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16451Y\"></sup>the companion of her youthand forgets <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16451Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16451Z\"></sup>the covenant of her God;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16452AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16452AA\"></sup>for her house sinks down to death,and her paths to the departed;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>none who go to her come back,nor do they regain the paths of life.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So you will walk in the way of the goodand keep to the paths of the righteous.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the upright <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16455AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16455AB\"></sup>will inhabit the land,and those with integrity will remain in it,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>but the wicked will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16456AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16456AC\"></sup>cut off from the land,and the treacherous will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16456AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16456AD\"></sup>rooted out of it."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16457A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16457A\"></sup>My son, do not forget my teaching,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16457B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16457B\"></sup>but let your heart keep my commandments,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16458C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16458C\"></sup>length of days and years of lifeand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16458D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16458D\"></sup>peace they will add to you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Let not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16459E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16459E\"></sup>steadfast love and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16459F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16459F\"></sup>faithfulness forsake you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16459G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16459G\"></sup>bind them around your neck;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16459H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16459H\"></sup>write them on the tablet of your heart.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16460I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16460I\"></sup>find favor and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16460J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16460J\"></sup>good successin the sight of God and man.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16461K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16461K\"></sup>Trust in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> with all your heart,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16461L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16461L\"></sup>do not lean on your own understanding.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In all your ways <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16462M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16462M\"></sup>acknowledge him,and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16462N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16462N\"></sup>will make straight your paths.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16463O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16463O\"></sup>Be not wise in your own eyes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16463P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16463P\"></sup>fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and turn away from evil.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>It will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16464Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16464Q\"></sup>healing to your fleshand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16464R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16464R\"></sup>refreshment to your bones.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Honor the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> with your wealthand with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16465S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16465S\"></sup>the firstfruits of all your produce;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>then your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16466T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16466T\"></sup>barns will be filled with plenty,and your vats will be bursting with wine.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16467U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16467U\"></sup>My son, do not despise the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s disciplineor be weary of his reproof,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> reproves him whom he loves,as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16468V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16468V\"></sup>a father the son in whom he delights.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16469W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16469W\"></sup>Blessed is the one who finds wisdom,and the one who gets understanding,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16470X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16470X\"></sup>for the gain from her is better than gain from silverand her profit better than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16470Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16470Y\"></sup>gold.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>She is more precious than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16471Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16471Z\"></sup>jewels,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16471AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16471AA\"></sup>nothing you desire can compare with her.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16472AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16472AB\"></sup>Long life is in her right hand;in her left hand are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16472AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16472AC\"></sup>riches and honor.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16473AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16473AD\"></sup>ways are ways of pleasantness,and all her paths are peace.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>She is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16474AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16474AE\"></sup>a tree of life to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16474AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16474AF\"></sup>lay hold of her;those who hold her fast are called blessed.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16475AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16475AG\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> by wisdom founded the earth;by understanding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16475AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16475AH\"></sup>he established the heavens;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>by his knowledge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16476AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16476AI\"></sup>the deeps broke open,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16476AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16476AJ\"></sup>the clouds drop down the dew.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16477AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16477AK\"></sup>do not lose sight of these—keep sound wisdom and discretion,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16478AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16478AL\"></sup>life for your souland <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16478AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16478AM\"></sup>adornment for your neck.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16479AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16479AN\"></sup>Then you will walk on your way securely,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16479AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16479AO\"></sup>and your foot will not stumble.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16480AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16480AP\"></sup>If you lie down, you will not be afraid;when you lie down, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16480AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16480AQ\"></sup>your sleep will be sweet.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16481AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16481AR\"></sup>Do not be afraid of sudden terroror of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16481AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16481AS\"></sup>the ruin of the wicked, when it comes,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be your confidenceand will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16482AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16482AT\"></sup>keep your foot from being caught.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16483AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16483AU\"></sup>Do not withhold good from those to whom it is due,when it is in your power to do it.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16484AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16484AV\"></sup>Do not say to your neighbor, “Go, and come again,tomorrow I will give it”—when you have it with you.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16485AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16485AW\"></sup>Do not plan evil against your neighbor,who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16485AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16485AX\"></sup>dwells trustingly beside you.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16486AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16486AY\"></sup>Do not contend with a man for no reason,when he has done you no harm.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16487AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16487AZ\"></sup>Do not envy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16487BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16487BA\"></sup>a man of violenceand do not choose any of his ways,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16488BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16488BB\"></sup>the devious person is an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,but the upright are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16488BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16488BC\"></sup>in his confidence.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16489BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16489BD\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s curse is on the house of the wicked,but he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16489BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16489BE\"></sup>blesses the dwelling of the righteous.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Toward the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16490BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16490BF\"></sup>scorners he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16490BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16490BG\"></sup>is scornful,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16490BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16490BH\"></sup>but to the humble he gives favor.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>The wise will inherit honor,but fools get disgrace."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16492A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16492A\"></sup>Hear, O sons, a father's instruction,and be attentive, that you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16492B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16492B\"></sup>gain insight,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for I give you good <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16493C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16493C\"></sup>precepts;do not forsake my teaching.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When I was a son with my father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16494D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16494D\"></sup>tender, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16494E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16494E\"></sup>the only one in the sight of my mother,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16495F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16495F\"></sup>taught me and said to me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16495G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16495G\"></sup>“Let your heart hold fast my words;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16495H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16495H\"></sup>keep my commandments, and live.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16496I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16496I\"></sup>Get wisdom; get <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16496J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16496J\"></sup>insight;do not forget, and do not turn away from the words of my mouth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not forsake her, and she will keep you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16497K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16497K\"></sup>love her, and she will guard you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16498L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16498L\"></sup>The beginning of wisdom is this: Get wisdom,and whatever you get, get <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16498M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16498M\"></sup>insight.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Prize her highly, and she will exalt you;she will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16499N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16499N\"></sup>honor you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16499O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16499O\"></sup>if you embrace her.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>She will place on your head <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16500P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16500P\"></sup>a graceful garland;she will bestow on you a beautiful crown.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16501Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16501Q\"></sup>Hear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16501R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16501R\"></sup>my son, and accept my words,that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16501S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16501S\"></sup>the years of your life may be many.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16502T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16502T\"></sup>taught you the way of wisdom;I have led you in the paths of uprightness.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When you walk, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16503U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16503U\"></sup>your step will not be hampered,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16503V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16503V\"></sup>if you run, you will not stumble.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16504W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16504W\"></sup>Keep hold of instruction; do not let go;guard her, for she is your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16504X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16504X\"></sup>life.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16505Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16505Y\"></sup>Do not enter the path of the wicked,and do not walk in the way of the evil.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Avoid it; do not go on it;turn away from it and pass on.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16507Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16507Z\"></sup>cannot sleep unless they have done wrong;they are robbed of sleep unless they have made someone stumble.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For they eat the bread of wickedness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16508AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16508AA\"></sup>and drink the wine of violence.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16509AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16509AB\"></sup>the path of the righteous is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16509AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16509AC\"></sup>the light of dawn,which shines <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16509AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16509AD\"></sup>brighter and brighter until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16509AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16509AE\"></sup>full day.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16510AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16510AF\"></sup>The way of the wicked is like deep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16510AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16510AG\"></sup>darkness;they do not know over what they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16510AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16510AH\"></sup>stumble.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16511AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16511AI\"></sup>My son, be attentive to my words;incline your ear to my sayings.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16512AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16512AJ\"></sup>Let them not escape from your sight;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16512AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16512AK\"></sup>keep them within your heart.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16513AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16513AL\"></sup>life to those who find them,and healing to all their flesh.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Keep your heart with all vigilance,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16514AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16514AM\"></sup>from it flow <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16514AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16514AN\"></sup>the springs of life.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Put away from you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16515AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16515AO\"></sup>crooked speech,and put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16515AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16515AP\"></sup>devious talk far from you.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16516AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16516AQ\"></sup>Let your eyes look directly forward,and your gaze be straight before you.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16517AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16517AR\"></sup>Ponder the path of your feet;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16517AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16517AS\"></sup>then all your ways will be sure.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16518AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16518AT\"></sup>Do not swerve to the right or to the left;turn your foot away from evil."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16519A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16519A\"></sup>My son, be attentive to my wisdom;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16519B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16519B\"></sup>incline your ear to my understanding,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>that you may keep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16520C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16520C\"></sup>discretion,and your lips may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16520D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16520D\"></sup>guard knowledge.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For the lips of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16521E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16521E\"></sup>a forbidden woman drip honey,and her speech is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16521F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16521F\"></sup>smoother than oil,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>but in the end she is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16522G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16522G\"></sup>bitter as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16522H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16522H\"></sup>wormwood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16522I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16522I\"></sup>sharp as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16522J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16522J\"></sup>a two-edged sword.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Her feet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16523K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16523K\"></sup>go down to death;her steps follow the path to Sheol;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16524L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16524L\"></sup>does not ponder the path of life;her ways wander, and she does not know it.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16525M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16525M\"></sup>now, O sons, listen to me,and do not depart from the words of my mouth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Keep your way far from her,and do not go near the door of her house,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>lest you give your honor to othersand your years to the merciless,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>lest strangers take their fill of your strength,and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16528N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16528N\"></sup>labors go to the house of a foreigner,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and at the end of your life you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16529O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16529O\"></sup>groan,when your flesh and body are consumed,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and you say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16530P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16530P\"></sup>“How I hated discipline,and my heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16530Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16530Q\"></sup>despised reproof!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I did not listen to the voice of my teachersor incline my ear to my instructors.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16532R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16532R\"></sup>I am at the brink of utter ruinin the assembled congregation.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Drink <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16533S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16533S\"></sup>water from your own cistern,flowing water from your own well.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Should your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16534T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16534T\"></sup>springs be scattered abroad,streams of water <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16534U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16534U\"></sup>in the streets?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16535V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16535V\"></sup>Let them be for yourself alone,and not for strangers with you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Let your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16536W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16536W\"></sup>fountain be blessed,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16536X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16536X\"></sup>rejoice in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16536Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16536Y\"></sup>the wife of your youth,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>a lovely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16537Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16537Z\"></sup>deer, a graceful doe.Let her breasts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16537AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16537AA\"></sup>fill you at all times with delight;be intoxicated always in her love.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Why should you be intoxicated, my son, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16538AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16538AB\"></sup>a forbidden womanand embrace the bosom of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16538AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16538AC\"></sup>an adulteress?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16539AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16539AD\"></sup>a man's ways are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16539AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16539AE\"></sup>before the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16539AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16539AF\"></sup>ponders all his paths.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16540AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16540AG\"></sup>iniquities of the wicked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16540AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16540AH\"></sup>ensnare him,and he is held fast in the cords of his sin.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16541AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16541AI\"></sup>He dies for lack of discipline,and because of his great folly he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16541AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16541AJ\"></sup>led astray."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>My son, if you have put up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16542A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16542A\"></sup>security for your neighbor,have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16542B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16542B\"></sup>given your pledge for a stranger,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>if you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16543C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16543C\"></sup>snared in the words of your mouth,caught in the words of your mouth,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>then do this, my son, and save yourself,for you have come into the hand of your neighbor:go, hasten, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16544D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16544D\"></sup>plead urgently with your neighbor.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16545E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16545E\"></sup>Give your eyes no sleepand your eyelids no slumber;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>save yourself like a gazelle from the hand of the hunter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16546F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16546F\"></sup>like a bird from the hand of the fowler.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16547G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16547G\"></sup>Go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16547H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16547H\"></sup>the ant, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16547I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16547I\"></sup>sluggard;consider her ways, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16547J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16547J\"></sup>be wise.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16548K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16548K\"></sup>Without having any chief,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16548L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16548L\"></sup>officer, or ruler,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>she prepares her bread <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16549M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16549M\"></sup>in summerand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16549N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16549N\"></sup>gathers her food in harvest.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16550O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16550O\"></sup>How long will you lie there, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16550P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16550P\"></sup>O sluggard?When will you arise from your sleep?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16551Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16551Q\"></sup>A little sleep, a little slumber,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16551R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16551R\"></sup>a little <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16551S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16551S\"></sup>folding of the hands to rest,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16552T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16552T\"></sup>and poverty will come upon you like a robber,and want like an armed man.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16553U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16553U\"></sup>A worthless person, a wicked man,goes about with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16553V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16553V\"></sup>crooked speech,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16554W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16554W\"></sup>winks with his eyes, signals with his feet,points with his finger,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16555X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16555X\"></sup>perverted heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16555Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16555Y\"></sup>devises evil,continually <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16555Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16555Z\"></sup>sowing discord;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>therefore calamity will come upon him suddenly;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16556AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16556AA\"></sup>in a moment he will be broken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16556AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16556AB\"></sup>beyond healing.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>There are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16557AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16557AC\"></sup>six things that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> hates,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16557AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16557AD\"></sup>seven that are an abomination to him:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16558AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16558AE\"></sup>haughty eyes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16558AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16558AF\"></sup>a lying tongue,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16558AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16558AG\"></sup>hands that shed innocent blood,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16559AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16559AH\"></sup>a heart that devises wicked plans,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16559AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16559AI\"></sup>feet that make haste to run to evil,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16560AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16560AJ\"></sup>a false witness who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16560AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16560AK\"></sup>breathes out lies,and one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16560AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16560AL\"></sup>sows discord among brothers.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16561AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16561AM\"></sup>My son, keep your father's commandment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16561AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16561AN\"></sup>and forsake not your mother's teaching.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16562AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16562AO\"></sup>Bind them on your heart always;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16562AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16562AP\"></sup>tie them around your neck.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16563AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16563AQ\"></sup>When you walk, they will lead you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16563AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16563AR\"></sup>when you lie down, they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16563AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16563AS\"></sup>watch over you;and when you awake, they will talk with you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For the commandment is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16564AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16564AT\"></sup>a lamp and the teaching a light,and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16564AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16564AU\"></sup>reproofs of discipline are the way of life,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>to preserve you from the evil woman,from the smooth tongue of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16565AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16565AV\"></sup>the adulteress.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16566AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16566AW\"></sup>Do not desire her beauty in your heart,and do not let her capture you with her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16566AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16566AX\"></sup>eyelashes;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16567AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16567AY\"></sup>the price of a prostitute is only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16567AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16567AZ\"></sup>a loaf of bread,but a married woman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16567BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16567BA\"></sup>hunts down a precious life.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Can a man carry <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16568BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16568BB\"></sup>fire next to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16568BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16568BC\"></sup>chestand his clothes not be burned?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Or can one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16569BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16569BD\"></sup>walk on hot coalsand his feet not be scorched?",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So is he who goes in to his neighbor's wife;none who touches her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16570BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16570BE\"></sup>will go unpunished.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>People do not despise a thief if he stealsto <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16571BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16571BF\"></sup>satisfy his appetite when he is hungry,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16572BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16572BG\"></sup>if he is caught, he will pay <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16572BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16572BH\"></sup>sevenfold;he will give all the goods of his house.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>He who commits adultery lacks sense;he who does it destroys himself.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>He will get wounds and dishonor,and his disgrace will not be wiped away.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16575BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16575BI\"></sup>jealousy makes a man furious,and he will not spare when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16575BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16575BJ\"></sup>he takes revenge.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>He will accept no compensation;he will refuse though you multiply gifts."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16577A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16577A\"></sup>My son, keep my wordsand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16577B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16577B\"></sup>treasure up my commandments with you;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16578C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16578C\"></sup>keep my commandments and live;keep my teaching as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16578D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16578D\"></sup>the apple of your eye;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16579E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16579E\"></sup>bind them on your fingers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16579F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16579F\"></sup>write them on the tablet of your heart.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Say to wisdom, “You are my sister,”and call insight your intimate friend,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>to keep you from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16581G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16581G\"></sup>the forbidden woman,from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16581H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16581H\"></sup>the adulteress with her smooth words.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16582I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16582I\"></sup>the window of my houseI have looked out through my lattice,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and I have seen among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16583J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16583J\"></sup>the simple,I have perceived among the youths,a young man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16583K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16583K\"></sup>lacking sense,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>passing along the street <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16584L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16584L\"></sup>near her corner,taking the road to her house",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16585M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16585M\"></sup>the twilight, in the evening,at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16585N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16585N\"></sup>the time of night and darkness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And behold, the woman meets him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16586O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16586O\"></sup>dressed as a prostitute, wily of heart.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>She is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16587P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16587P\"></sup>loud and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16587Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16587Q\"></sup>wayward;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16587R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16587R\"></sup>her feet do not stay at home;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>now in the street, now in the market,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16588S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16588S\"></sup>at every corner she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16588T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16588T\"></sup>lies in wait.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>She seizes him and kisses him,and with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16589U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16589U\"></sup>bold face she says to him,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“I had to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16590V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16590V\"></sup>offer sacrifices,and today I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16590W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16590W\"></sup>paid my vows;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>so now I have come out to meet you,to seek you eagerly, and I have found you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I have spread my couch with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16592X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16592X\"></sup>coverings,colored linens from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16592Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16592Y\"></sup>Egyptian linen;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I have perfumed my bed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16593Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16593Z\"></sup>myrrh,aloes, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16593AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16593AA\"></sup>cinnamon.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Come, let us take our fill of love till morning;let us delight ourselves with love.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16595AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16595AB\"></sup>my husband is not at home;he has gone on a long journey;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>he took a bag of money with him;at full moon he will come home.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>With much seductive speech she persuades him;with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16597AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16597AC\"></sup>her smooth talk she compels him.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>All at once he follows her,as an ox goes to the slaughter,or as a stag is caught fast",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>till an arrow pierces its liver;as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16599AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16599AD\"></sup>a bird rushes into a snare;he does not know that it will cost him his life.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16600AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16600AE\"></sup>now, O sons, listen to me,and be attentive to the words of my mouth.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Let not your heart turn aside to her ways;do not stray into her paths,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>for many a victim has she laid low,and all her slain are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16602AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16602AF\"></sup>a mighty throng.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Her house is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16603AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16603AG\"></sup>the way to Sheol,going down to the chambers of death."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16604A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16604A\"></sup>wisdom call?Does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16604B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16604B\"></sup>understanding raise her voice?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>On <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16605C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16605C\"></sup>the heights beside the way,at the crossroads she takes her stand;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>beside <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16606D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16606D\"></sup>the gates in front of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16606E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16606E\"></sup>the town,at the entrance of the portals she cries aloud:",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“To you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16607F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16607F\"></sup>men, I call,and my cry is to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16607G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16607G\"></sup>the children of man.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16608H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16608H\"></sup>simple ones, learn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16608I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16608I\"></sup>prudence;O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16608J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16608J\"></sup>fools, learn sense.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Hear, for I will speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16609K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16609K\"></sup>noble things,and from my lips will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16609L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16609L\"></sup>what is right,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>for my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16610M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16610M\"></sup>mouth will utter truth;wickedness is an abomination to my lips.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>All the words of my mouth are righteous;there is nothing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16611N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16611N\"></sup>twisted or crooked in them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They are all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16612O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16612O\"></sup>straight to him who understands,and right to those who find knowledge.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16613P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16613P\"></sup>Take my instruction instead of silver,and knowledge rather than choice gold,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16614Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16614Q\"></sup>for wisdom is better than jewels,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16614R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16614R\"></sup>all that you may desire cannot compare with her.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I, wisdom, dwell with prudence,and I find knowledge and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16615S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16615S\"></sup>discretion.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16616T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16616T\"></sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16616U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16616U\"></sup>hatred of evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16616V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16616V\"></sup>Pride and arrogance and the way of eviland <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16616W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16616W\"></sup>perverted speech I hate.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16617X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16617X\"></sup>counsel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16617Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16617Y\"></sup>sound wisdom;I have insight; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16617Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16617Z\"></sup>I have strength.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>By me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16618AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16618AA\"></sup>kings reign,and rulers decree what is just;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>by me princes rule,and nobles, all who govern justly.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16620AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16620AB\"></sup>I love those who love me,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16620AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16620AC\"></sup>those who seek me diligently find me.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16621AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16621AD\"></sup>Riches and honor are with me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16621AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16621AE\"></sup>enduring wealth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16621AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16621AF\"></sup>righteousness.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>My fruit is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16622AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16622AG\"></sup>better than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16622AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16622AH\"></sup>gold, even fine gold,and my yield than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16622AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16622AI\"></sup>choice silver.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I walk in the way of righteousness,in the paths of justice,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>granting an inheritance to those who love me,and filling their treasuries.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16625AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16625AJ\"></sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16625AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16625AK\"></sup>possessed me at the beginning of his work,the first of his acts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16625AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16625AL\"></sup>of old.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Ages ago I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16626AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16626AM\"></sup>set up,at the first, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16626AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16626AN\"></sup>before the beginning of the earth.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When there were no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16627AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16627AO\"></sup>depths I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16627AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16627AP\"></sup>brought forth,when there were no springs abounding with water.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Before the mountains <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16628AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16628AQ\"></sup>had been shaped,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16628AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16628AR\"></sup>before the hills, I was brought forth,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>before he had made the earth with its fields,or the first of the dust of the world.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16630AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16630AS\"></sup>established the heavens, I was there;when he drew <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16630AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16630AT\"></sup>a circle on the face of the deep,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16631AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16631AU\"></sup>made firm the skies above,when he established the fountains of the deep,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16632AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16632AV\"></sup>assigned to the sea its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16632AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16632AW\"></sup>limit,so that the waters might not transgress his command,when he marked out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16632AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16632AX\"></sup>the foundations of the earth,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16633AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16633AY\"></sup>I was beside him, like a master workman,and I was daily his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16633AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16633AZ\"></sup>delight,rejoicing before him always,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16634BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16634BA\"></sup>rejoicing in his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16634BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16634BB\"></sup>inhabited worldand delighting in the children of man.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“And now, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16635BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16635BC\"></sup>O sons, listen to me:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16635BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16635BD\"></sup>blessed are those who keep my ways.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16636BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16636BE\"></sup>Hear instruction and be wise,and do not neglect it.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16637BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16637BF\"></sup>Blessed is the one who listens to me,watching daily at my gates,waiting beside my doors.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16638BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16638BG\"></sup>whoever finds me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16638BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16638BH\"></sup>finds lifeand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16638BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16638BI\"></sup>obtains favor from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>but he who fails to find me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16639BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16639BJ\"></sup>injures himself;all who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16639BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16639BK\"></sup>hate me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16639BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16639BL\"></sup>love death.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16640A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16640A\"></sup>Wisdom has built her house;she has hewn her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16640B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16640B\"></sup>seven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16640C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16640C\"></sup>pillars.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>She has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16641D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16641D\"></sup>slaughtered her beasts; she has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16641E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16641E\"></sup>mixed her wine;she has also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16641F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16641F\"></sup>set her table.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>She has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16642G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16642G\"></sup>sent out her young women to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16642H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16642H\"></sup>callfrom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16642I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16642I\"></sup>the highest places in the town,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16643J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16643J\"></sup>“Whoever is simple, let him turn in here!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16643K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16643K\"></sup>To him who lacks sense she says,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Come, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16644L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16644L\"></sup>eat of my breadand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16644M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16644M\"></sup>drink of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16644N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16644N\"></sup>the wine I have mixed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Leave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16645O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16645O\"></sup>your simple ways, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16645P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16645P\"></sup>live,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16645Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16645Q\"></sup>and walk in the way of insight.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Whoever corrects a scoffer gets himself abuse,and he who reproves a wicked man incurs injury.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16647R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16647R\"></sup>Do not reprove a scoffer, or he will hate you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16647S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16647S\"></sup>reprove a wise man, and he will love you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Give instruction to a wise man, and he will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16648T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16648T\"></sup>still wiser;teach a righteous man, and he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16648U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16648U\"></sup>increase in learning.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16649V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16649V\"></sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the beginning of wisdom,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16649W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16649W\"></sup>the knowledge of the Holy One is insight.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For by me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16650X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16650X\"></sup>your days will be multiplied,and years will be added to your life.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16651Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16651Y\"></sup>If you are wise, you are wise for yourself;if you scoff, you alone will bear it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16652Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16652Z\"></sup>The woman Folly is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16652AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16652AA\"></sup>loud;she is seductive and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16652AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16652AB\"></sup>knows nothing.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>She sits at the door of her house;she takes a seat on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16653AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16653AC\"></sup>the highest places of the town,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>calling to those who pass by,who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16654AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16654AD\"></sup>going straight on their way,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16655AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16655AE\"></sup>“Whoever is simple, let him turn in here!”And to him who lacks sense she says,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16656AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16656AF\"></sup>“Stolen water is sweet,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16656AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16656AG\"></sup>bread eaten in secret is pleasant.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But he does not know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16657AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16657AH\"></sup>that the dead are there,that her guests are in the depths of Sheol."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16658A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16658A\"></sup>The proverbs of Solomon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16658B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16658B\"></sup>A wise son makes a glad father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16658C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16658C\"></sup>but a foolish son is a sorrow to his mother.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16659D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16659D\"></sup>Treasures gained by wickedness do not profit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16659E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16659E\"></sup>but righteousness delivers from death.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16660F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16660F\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does not let the righteous go hungry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16660G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16660G\"></sup>but he thwarts the craving of the wicked.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>A slack hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16661H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16661H\"></sup>causes poverty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16661I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16661I\"></sup>but the hand of the diligent makes rich.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16662J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16662J\"></sup>gathers in summer is a prudent son,but he who sleeps in harvest is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16662K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16662K\"></sup>a son who brings shame.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Blessings are on the head of the righteous,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16663L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16663L\"></sup>the mouth of the wicked conceals violence.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16664M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16664M\"></sup>The memory of the righteous is a blessing,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16664N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16664N\"></sup>the name of the wicked will rot.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16665O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16665O\"></sup>The wise of heart will receive commandments,but a babbling fool will come to ruin.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16666P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16666P\"></sup>Whoever walks in integrity walks securely,but he who makes his ways crooked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16666Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16666Q\"></sup>will be found out.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16667R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16667R\"></sup>winks the eye causes trouble,and a babbling fool will come to ruin.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16668S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16668S\"></sup>The mouth of the righteous is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16668T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16668T\"></sup>a fountain of life,but the mouth of the wicked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16668U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16668U\"></sup>conceals violence.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Hatred stirs up strife,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16669V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16669V\"></sup>love covers all offenses.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>On the lips of him who has understanding, wisdom is found,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16670W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16670W\"></sup>a rod is for the back of him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16670X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16670X\"></sup>lacks sense.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The wise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16671Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16671Y\"></sup>lay up knowledge,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16671Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16671Z\"></sup>the mouth of a fool brings ruin near.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16672AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16672AA\"></sup>A rich man's wealth is his strong city;the poverty of the poor is their ruin.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The wage of the righteous leads <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16673AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16673AB\"></sup>to life,the gain of the wicked to sin.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Whoever heeds instruction is on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16674AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16674AC\"></sup>the path to life,but he who rejects reproof leads others astray.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The one who conceals hatred has lying lips,and whoever utters slander is a fool.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16676AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16676AD\"></sup>When words are many, transgression is not lacking,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16676AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16676AE\"></sup>but whoever restrains his lips is prudent.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The tongue of the righteous is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16677AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16677AF\"></sup>choice silver;the heart of the wicked is of little worth.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The lips of the righteous feed many,but fools die for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16678AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16678AG\"></sup>lack of sense.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16679AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16679AH\"></sup>The blessing of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> makes rich,and he adds no sorrow with it.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Doing wrong is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16680AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16680AI\"></sup>like a joke to a fool,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16680AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16680AJ\"></sup>wisdom is pleasure to a man of understanding.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16681AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16681AK\"></sup>What the wicked dreads <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16681AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16681AL\"></sup>will come upon him,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16681AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16681AM\"></sup>the desire of the righteous will be granted.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16682AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16682AN\"></sup>the tempest passes, the wicked is no more,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16682AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16682AO\"></sup>the righteous is established forever.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Like vinegar to the teeth and smoke to the eyes,so is the sluggard to those who send him.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16684AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16684AP\"></sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> prolongs life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16684AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16684AQ\"></sup>but the years of the wicked will be short.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16685AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16685AR\"></sup>The hope of the righteous brings joy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16685AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16685AS\"></sup>but the expectation of the wicked will perish.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16686AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16686AT\"></sup>The way of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a stronghold to the blameless,but destruction to evildoers.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16687AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16687AU\"></sup>The righteous will never be removed,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16687AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16687AV\"></sup>the wicked will not dwell in the land.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16688AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16688AW\"></sup>The mouth of the righteous brings forth wisdom,but the perverse tongue will be cut off.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>The lips of the righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16689AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16689AX\"></sup>know what is acceptable,but the mouth of the wicked, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16689AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16689AY\"></sup>what is perverse."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16690A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16690A\"></sup>A false balance is an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16690B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16690B\"></sup>but a just weight is his delight.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16691C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16691C\"></sup>When pride comes, then comes disgrace,but with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16691D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16691D\"></sup>the humble is wisdom.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16692E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16692E\"></sup>The integrity of the upright guides them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16692F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16692F\"></sup>but the crookedness of the treacherous destroys them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16693G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16693G\"></sup>Riches do not profit in the day of wrath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16693H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16693H\"></sup>but righteousness delivers from death.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The righteousness of the blameless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16694I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16694I\"></sup>keeps his way straight,but the wicked falls by his own wickedness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16695J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16695J\"></sup>The righteousness of the upright delivers them,but the treacherous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16695K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16695K\"></sup>are taken captive by their lust.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the wicked dies, his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16696L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16696L\"></sup>hope will perish,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16696M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16696M\"></sup>the expectation of wealth perishes too.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16697N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16697N\"></sup>The righteous is delivered from trouble,and the wicked walks into it instead.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>With his mouth the godless man would destroy his neighbor,but by knowledge the righteous are delivered.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16699O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16699O\"></sup>When it goes well with the righteous, the city rejoices,and when the wicked perish there are shouts of gladness.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>By the blessing of the upright a city is exalted,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16700P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16700P\"></sup>by the mouth of the wicked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16700Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16700Q\"></sup>it is overthrown.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16701R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16701R\"></sup>belittles his neighbor lacks sense,but a man of understanding remains silent.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16702S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16702S\"></sup>goes about slandering reveals secrets,but he who is trustworthy in spirit keeps a thing covered.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Where there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16703T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16703T\"></sup>no guidance, a people falls,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16703U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16703U\"></sup>but in an abundance of counselors there is safety.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16704V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16704V\"></sup>Whoever puts up security for a stranger will surely suffer harm,but he who hates striking hands in pledge is secure.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16705W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16705W\"></sup>A gracious woman gets honor,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16705X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16705X\"></sup>violent men get riches.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16706Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16706Y\"></sup>A man who is kind benefits himself,but a cruel man hurts himself.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The wicked earns deceptive wages,but one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16707Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16707Z\"></sup>sows righteousness gets a sure reward.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Whoever is steadfast in righteousness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16708AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16708AA\"></sup>will live,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16708AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16708AB\"></sup>he who pursues evil will die.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Those of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16709AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16709AC\"></sup>crooked heart are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16709AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16709AD\"></sup>an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,but those of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16709AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16709AE\"></sup>blameless ways are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16709AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16709AF\"></sup>his delight.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16710AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16710AG\"></sup>Be assured, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16710AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16710AH\"></sup>an evil person will not go unpunished,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16710AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16710AI\"></sup>the offspring of the righteous will be delivered.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16711AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16711AJ\"></sup>a gold ring in a pig's snoutis a beautiful woman without discretion.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The desire of the righteous ends only in good,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16712AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16712AK\"></sup>the expectation of the wicked in wrath.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16713AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16713AL\"></sup>One gives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16713AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16713AM\"></sup>freely, yet grows all the richer;another withholds what he should give, and only suffers want.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16714AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16714AN\"></sup>Whoever brings blessing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16714AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16714AO\"></sup>will be enriched,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16714AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16714AP\"></sup>one who waters will himself be watered.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16715AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16715AQ\"></sup>The people curse him who holds back grain,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16715AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16715AR\"></sup>a blessing is on the head of him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16715AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16715AS\"></sup>sells it.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Whoever diligently seeks good seeks favor,but evil comes to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16716AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16716AT\"></sup>him who searches for it.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16717AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16717AU\"></sup>trusts in his riches will fall,but the righteous will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16717AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16717AV\"></sup>flourish like a green leaf.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16718AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16718AW\"></sup>troubles his own household will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16718AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16718AX\"></sup>inherit the wind,and the fool will be servant to the wise of heart.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The fruit of the righteous is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16719AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16719AY\"></sup>a tree of life,and whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16719AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16719AZ\"></sup>captures souls is wise.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>If <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16720BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16720BA\"></sup>the righteous is repaid on earth,how much more the wicked and the sinner!"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Whoever loves discipline loves knowledge,but he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16721A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16721A\"></sup>hates reproof is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16721B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16721B\"></sup>stupid.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A good man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16722C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16722C\"></sup>obtains favor from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,but a man of evil devices he condemns.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>No one is established by wickedness,but the root of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16723D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16723D\"></sup>the righteous will never be moved.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16724E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16724E\"></sup>An excellent wife is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16724F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16724F\"></sup>the crown of her husband,but she who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16724G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16724G\"></sup>brings shame is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16724H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16724H\"></sup>rottenness in his bones.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16725I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16725I\"></sup>The thoughts of the righteous are just;the counsels of the wicked are deceitful.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The words of the wicked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16726J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16726J\"></sup>lie in wait for blood,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16726K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16726K\"></sup>the mouth of the upright delivers them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16727L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16727L\"></sup>The wicked are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16727M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16727M\"></sup>overthrown and are no more,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16727N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16727N\"></sup>but the house of the righteous will stand.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>A man is commended according to his good sense,but one of twisted mind is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16728O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16728O\"></sup>despised.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Better to be lowly and have a servantthan to play the great man and lack bread.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16730P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16730P\"></sup>Whoever is righteous has regard for the life of his beast,but the mercy of the wicked is cruel.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16731Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16731Q\"></sup>Whoever works his land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16731R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16731R\"></sup>will have plenty of bread,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16731S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16731S\"></sup>but he who follows <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16731T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16731T\"></sup>worthless pursuits lacks sense.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Whoever is wicked covets <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16732U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16732U\"></sup>the spoil of evildoers,but the root of the righteous bears fruit.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>An evil man is ensnared <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16733V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16733V\"></sup>by the transgression of his lips,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16733W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16733W\"></sup>but the righteous escapes from trouble.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>From the fruit of his mouth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16734X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16734X\"></sup>a man is satisfied with good,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16734Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16734Y\"></sup>and the work of a man's hand comes back to him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16735Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16735Z\"></sup>The way of a fool is right in his own eyes,but a wise man listens to advice.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16736AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16736AA\"></sup>The vexation of a fool is known at once,but the prudent ignores an insult.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16737AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16737AB\"></sup>Whoever speaks the truth gives honest evidence,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16737AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16737AC\"></sup>a false witness utters deceit.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16738AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16738AD\"></sup>There is one whose rash words are like sword thrusts,but the tongue of the wise brings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16738AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16738AE\"></sup>healing.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Truthful lips endure forever,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16739AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16739AF\"></sup>a lying tongue is but for a moment.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Deceit is in the heart of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16740AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16740AG\"></sup>those who devise evil,but those who plan peace have joy.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16741AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16741AH\"></sup>No ill befalls the righteous,but the wicked are filled with trouble.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16742AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16742AI\"></sup>Lying lips are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16742AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16742AJ\"></sup>an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16742AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16742AK\"></sup>but those who act faithfully are his delight.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16743AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16743AL\"></sup>A prudent man conceals knowledge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16743AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16743AM\"></sup>but the heart of fools proclaims folly.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16744AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16744AN\"></sup>The hand of the diligent will rule,while the slothful will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16744AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16744AO\"></sup>put to forced labor.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16745AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16745AP\"></sup>Anxiety in a man's heart weighs him down,but a good word makes him glad.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>One who is righteous is a guide to his neighbor,but the way of the wicked leads them astray.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16747AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16747AQ\"></sup>Whoever is slothful will not roast his game,but the diligent man will get precious wealth.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16748AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16748AR\"></sup>In the path of righteousness is life,and in its pathway there is no death."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>A wise son hears his father's instruction,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16749A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16749A\"></sup>a scoffer does not listen to rebuke.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>From the fruit of his mouth a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16750B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16750B\"></sup>eats what is good,but the desire of the treacherous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16750C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16750C\"></sup>is for violence.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16751D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16751D\"></sup>Whoever guards his mouth preserves his life;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16751E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16751E\"></sup>he who opens wide his lips <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16751F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16751F\"></sup>comes to ruin.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16752G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16752G\"></sup>The soul of the sluggard craves and gets nothing,while the soul of the diligent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16752H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16752H\"></sup>is richly supplied.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The righteous hates falsehood,but the wicked brings shame and disgrace.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16754I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16754I\"></sup>Righteousness guards him whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16754J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16754J\"></sup>way is blameless,but sin overthrows the wicked.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16755K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16755K\"></sup>One pretends to be rich, yet has nothing;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16755L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16755L\"></sup>another pretends to be poor, yet has great wealth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The ransom of a man's life is his wealth,but a poor man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16756M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16756M\"></sup>hears no threat.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16757N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16757N\"></sup>The light of the righteous rejoices,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16757O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16757O\"></sup>the lamp of the wicked will be put out.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16758P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16758P\"></sup>By insolence comes nothing but strife,but with those who take advice is wisdom.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16759Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16759Q\"></sup>Wealth gained hastily will dwindle,but whoever gathers little by little will increase it.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Hope deferred makes the heart sick,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16760R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16760R\"></sup>but a desire fulfilled is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16760S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16760S\"></sup>a tree of life.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16761T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16761T\"></sup>despises <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16761U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16761U\"></sup>the word brings destruction on himself,but he who reveres the commandment will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16761V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16761V\"></sup>rewarded.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The teaching of the wise is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16762W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16762W\"></sup>a fountain of life,that one may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16762X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16762X\"></sup>turn away from the snares of death.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16763Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16763Y\"></sup>Good sense wins <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16763Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16763Z\"></sup>favor,but the way of the treacherous is their ruin.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16764AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16764AA\"></sup>Every prudent man acts with knowledge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16764AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16764AB\"></sup>but a fool flaunts his folly.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>A wicked messenger falls into trouble,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16765AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16765AC\"></sup>a faithful envoy brings healing.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Poverty and disgrace come to him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16766AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16766AD\"></sup>ignores instruction,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16766AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16766AE\"></sup>but whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16766AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16766AF\"></sup>heeds reproof is honored.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16767AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16767AG\"></sup>A desire fulfilled is sweet to the soul,but to turn away from evil is an abomination to fools.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Whoever walks with the wise becomes wise,but the companion of fools will suffer harm.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16769AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16769AH\"></sup>Disaster pursues sinners,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16769AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16769AI\"></sup>but the righteous are rewarded with good.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16770AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16770AJ\"></sup>A good man leaves an inheritance to his children's children,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16770AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16770AK\"></sup>the sinner's wealth is laid up for the righteous.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The fallow ground of the poor would yield much food,but it is swept away through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16771AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16771AL\"></sup>injustice.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16772AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16772AM\"></sup>Whoever spares the rod hates his son,but he who loves him is diligent to discipline him.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16773AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16773AN\"></sup>The righteous has enough to satisfy his appetite,but the belly of the wicked suffers want."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16774A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16774A\"></sup>The wisest of women <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16774B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16774B\"></sup>builds her house,but folly with her own hands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16774C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16774C\"></sup>tears it down.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16775D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16775D\"></sup>walks in uprightness fears the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,but he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16775E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16775E\"></sup>devious in his ways despises him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>By the mouth of a fool comes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16776F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16776F\"></sup>a rod for his back,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16776G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16776G\"></sup>but the lips of the wise will preserve them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Where there are no oxen, the manger is clean,but abundant crops come by the strength of the ox.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16778H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16778H\"></sup>A faithful witness does not lie,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16778I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16778I\"></sup>a false witness breathes out lies.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16779J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16779J\"></sup>A scoffer seeks wisdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16779K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16779K\"></sup>in vain,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16779L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16779L\"></sup>knowledge is easy for a man of understanding.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Leave the presence of a fool,for there you do not meet words of knowledge.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The wisdom of the prudent is to discern his way,but the folly of fools is deceiving.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16782M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16782M\"></sup>Fools mock at the guilt offering,but the upright enjoy acceptance.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The heart knows its own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16783N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16783N\"></sup>bitterness,and no stranger shares its joy.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16784O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16784O\"></sup>The house of the wicked will be destroyed,but the tent of the upright will flourish.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16785P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16785P\"></sup>There is a way that seems right to a man,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16785Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16785Q\"></sup>its end is the way to death.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Even in laughter the heart may ache,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16786R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16786R\"></sup>the end of joy may be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16786S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16786S\"></sup>grief.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The backslider in heart will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16787T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16787T\"></sup>filled with the fruit of his ways,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16787U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16787U\"></sup>a good man will be filled with the fruit of his ways.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16788V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16788V\"></sup>The simple believes everything,but the prudent gives thought to his steps.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16789W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16789W\"></sup>One who is wise is cautious and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16789X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16789X\"></sup>turns away from evil,but a fool is reckless and careless.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>A man of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16790Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16790Y\"></sup>quick temper acts foolishly,and a man of evil devices is hated.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The simple inherit folly,but the prudent are crowned with knowledge.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16792Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16792Z\"></sup>The evil bow down before the good,the wicked at the gates of the righteous.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16793AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16793AA\"></sup>The poor is disliked even by his neighbor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16793AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16793AB\"></sup>but the rich has many friends.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16794AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16794AC\"></sup>despises his neighbor is a sinner,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16794AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16794AD\"></sup>blessed is he who is generous to the poor.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Do they not go astray who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16795AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16795AE\"></sup>devise evil?Those who devise good meet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16795AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16795AF\"></sup>steadfast love and faithfulness.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>In all toil there is profit,but mere talk <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16796AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16796AG\"></sup>tends only to poverty.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The crown of the wise is their wealth,but the folly of fools brings folly.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>A truthful witness saves lives,but one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16798AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16798AH\"></sup>breathes out lies is deceitful.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>In the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> one has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16799AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16799AI\"></sup>strong confidence,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16799AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16799AJ\"></sup>his children will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16799AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16799AK\"></sup>a refuge.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16800AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16800AL\"></sup>a fountain of life,that one may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16800AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16800AM\"></sup>turn away from the snares of death.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16801AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16801AN\"></sup>a multitude of people is the glory of a king,but without people a prince is ruined.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Whoever is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16802AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16802AO\"></sup>slow to anger has great understanding,but he who has a hasty temper exalts folly.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>A tranquil heart gives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16803AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16803AP\"></sup>life to the flesh,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16803AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16803AQ\"></sup>envy makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16803AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16803AR\"></sup>the bones rot.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Whoever oppresses a poor man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16804AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16804AS\"></sup>insults his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16804AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16804AT\"></sup>Maker,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16804AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16804AU\"></sup>but he who is generous to the needy honors him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16805AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16805AV\"></sup>The wicked is overthrown through his evildoing,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16805AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16805AW\"></sup>the righteous finds refuge in his death.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Wisdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16806AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16806AX\"></sup>rests in the heart of a man of understanding,but it makes itself known even in the midst of fools.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Righteousness exalts a nation,but sin is a reproach to any people.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>A servant who deals wisely has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16808AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16808AY\"></sup>the king's favor,but his wrath falls on one who acts shamefully."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16809A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16809A\"></sup>A soft answer turns away wrath,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16809B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16809B\"></sup>a harsh word stirs up anger.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The tongue of the wise commends knowledge,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16810C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16810C\"></sup>the mouths of fools pour out folly.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16811D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16811D\"></sup>The eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> are in every place,keeping watch on the evil and the good.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16812E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16812E\"></sup>A gentle tongue is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16812F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16812F\"></sup>a tree of life,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16812G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16812G\"></sup>perverseness in it breaks the spirit.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16813H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16813H\"></sup>A fool <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16813I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16813I\"></sup>despises his father's instruction,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16813J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16813J\"></sup>whoever heeds reproof is prudent.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In the house of the righteous there is much treasure,but trouble befalls the income of the wicked.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16815K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16815K\"></sup>The lips of the wise spread knowledge;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16815L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16815L\"></sup>not so the hearts of fools.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16816M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16816M\"></sup>The sacrifice of the wicked is an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16816N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16816N\"></sup>the prayer of the upright is acceptable to him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The way of the wicked is an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,but he loves him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16817O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16817O\"></sup>who pursues righteousness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16818P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16818P\"></sup>severe discipline for him who forsakes the way;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16818Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16818Q\"></sup>whoever hates reproof will die.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Sheol and Abaddon lie open before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;how much more <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16819R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16819R\"></sup>the hearts of the children of man!",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16820S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16820S\"></sup>A scoffer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16820T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16820T\"></sup>does not like to be reproved;he will not go to the wise.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16821U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16821U\"></sup>A glad heart makes a cheerful face,but by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16821V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16821V\"></sup>sorrow of heart the spirit is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16821W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16821W\"></sup>crushed.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16822X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16822X\"></sup>The heart of him who has understanding seeks knowledge,but the mouths of fools feed on folly.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>All the days of the afflicted are evil,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16823Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16823Y\"></sup>the cheerful of heart has a continual feast.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16824Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16824Z\"></sup>Better is a little with the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>than great treasure and trouble with it.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16825AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16825AA\"></sup>Better is a dinner of herbs where love isthan <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16825AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16825AB\"></sup>a fattened ox and hatred with it.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16826AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16826AC\"></sup>A hot-tempered man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16826AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16826AD\"></sup>stirs up strife,but he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16826AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16826AE\"></sup>slow to anger quiets contention.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The way of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16827AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16827AF\"></sup>a sluggard is like a hedge of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16827AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16827AG\"></sup>thorns,but the path of the upright is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16827AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16827AH\"></sup>a level highway.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16828AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16828AI\"></sup>A wise son makes a glad father,but a foolish man despises his mother.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16829AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16829AJ\"></sup>Folly is a joy to him who lacks sense,but a man of understanding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16829AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16829AK\"></sup>walks straight ahead.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16830AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16830AL\"></sup>Without counsel plans fail,but with many advisers they succeed.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>To make an apt answer is a joy to a man,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16831AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16831AM\"></sup>a word in season, how good it is!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The path of life leads upward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16832AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16832AN\"></sup>for the prudent,that he may turn away from Sheol beneath.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> tears down the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16833AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16833AO\"></sup>the proudbut <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16833AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16833AP\"></sup>maintains <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16833AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16833AQ\"></sup>the widow's boundaries.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16834AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16834AR\"></sup>The thoughts of the wicked are an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16834AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16834AS\"></sup>gracious words are pure.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Whoever is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16835AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16835AT\"></sup>greedy for unjust gain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16835AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16835AU\"></sup>troubles his own household,but he who hates <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16835AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16835AV\"></sup>bribes will live.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The heart of the righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16836AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16836AW\"></sup>ponders how to answer,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16836AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16836AX\"></sup>the mouth of the wicked pours out evil things.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16837AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16837AY\"></sup>far from the wicked,but he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16837AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16837AZ\"></sup>hears the prayer of the righteous.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16838BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16838BA\"></sup>The light of the eyes rejoices the heart,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16838BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16838BB\"></sup>good news refreshes the bones.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16839BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16839BC\"></sup>The ear that listens to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16839BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16839BD\"></sup>life-giving reproofwill dwell among the wise.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16840BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16840BE\"></sup>ignores instruction <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16840BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16840BF\"></sup>despises himself,but he who listens to reproof <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16840BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16840BG\"></sup>gains intelligence.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16841BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16841BH\"></sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is instruction in wisdom,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16841BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16841BI\"></sup>humility comes before honor."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>The plans of the heart belong to man,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16842A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16842A\"></sup>the answer of the tongue is from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16843B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16843B\"></sup>All the ways of a man are pure in his own eyes,but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16843C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16843C\"></sup>weighs the spirit.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16844D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16844D\"></sup>Commit your work to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and your plans will be established.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16845E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16845E\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has made everything for its purpose,even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16845F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16845F\"></sup>the wicked for the day of trouble.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Everyone who is arrogant in heart is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16846G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16846G\"></sup>an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16846H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16846H\"></sup>be assured, he will not go unpunished.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>By <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16847I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16847I\"></sup>steadfast love and faithfulness iniquity is atoned for,and by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16847J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16847J\"></sup>the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16847K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16847K\"></sup>turns away from evil.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When a man's ways please the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16848L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16848L\"></sup>he makes even his enemies to be at peace with him.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16849M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16849M\"></sup>Better is a little with righteousnessthan great revenues with injustice.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16850N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16850N\"></sup>The heart of man plans his way,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16850O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16850O\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> establishes his steps.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16851P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16851P\"></sup>An oracle is on the lips of a king;his mouth does not sin in judgment.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16852Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16852Q\"></sup>A just balance and scales are the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s;all the weights in the bag are his work.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It is an abomination to kings to do evil,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16853R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16853R\"></sup>the throne is established by righteousness.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16854S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16854S\"></sup>Righteous lips are the delight of a king,and he loves him who speaks what is right.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16855T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16855T\"></sup>A king's wrath is a messenger of death,and a wise man will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16855U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16855U\"></sup>appease it.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16856V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16856V\"></sup>In the light of a king's face there is life,and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16856W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16856W\"></sup>favor is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16856X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16856X\"></sup>the clouds that bring the spring rain.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16857Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16857Y\"></sup>How much better to get wisdom than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16857Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16857Z\"></sup>gold!To get understanding is to be chosen rather than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16857AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16857AA\"></sup>silver.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The highway of the upright <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16858AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16858AB\"></sup>turns aside from evil;whoever guards his way preserves his life.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16859AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16859AC\"></sup>Pride goes before destruction,and a haughty spirit before a fall.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16860AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16860AD\"></sup>It is better to be of a lowly spirit with the poorthan to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16860AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16860AE\"></sup>divide the spoil with the proud.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Whoever gives thought to the word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16861AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16861AF\"></sup>will discover good,and blessed is he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16861AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16861AG\"></sup>who trusts in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The wise of heart is called discerning,and sweetness of speech <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16862AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16862AH\"></sup>increases persuasiveness.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Good sense is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16863AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16863AI\"></sup>a fountain of life to him who has it,but the instruction of fools is folly.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16864AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16864AJ\"></sup>The heart of the wise makes his speech judiciousand adds persuasiveness to his lips.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16865AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16865AK\"></sup>Gracious words are like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16865AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16865AL\"></sup>a honeycomb,sweetness to the soul and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16865AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16865AM\"></sup>health to the body.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>There is a way that seems right to a man,but its end is the way to death.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>A worker's appetite works for him;his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16867AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16867AN\"></sup>mouth urges him on.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16868AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16868AO\"></sup>A worthless man plots evil,and his speech is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16868AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16868AP\"></sup>a scorching fire.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16869AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16869AQ\"></sup>A dishonest man spreads strife,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16869AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16869AR\"></sup>a whisperer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16869AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16869AS\"></sup>separates close friends.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>A man of violence <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16870AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16870AT\"></sup>entices his neighborand leads him in a way that is not good.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Whoever winks his eyes plans <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16871AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16871AU\"></sup>dishonest things;he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16871AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16871AV\"></sup>purses his lips brings evil to pass.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16872AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16872AW\"></sup>Gray hair is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16872AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16872AX\"></sup>a crown of glory;it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16872AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16872AY\"></sup>is gained in a righteous life.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16873AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16873AZ\"></sup>Whoever is slow to anger is better than the mighty,and he who rules his spirit than he who takes a city.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16874BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16874BA\"></sup>The lot is cast into the lap,but its every decision is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16874BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16874BB\"></sup>from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16875A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16875A\"></sup>Better is a dry morsel with quietthan a house full of feasting with strife.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A servant who deals wisely will rule over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16876B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16876B\"></sup>a son who acts shamefullyand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16876C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16876C\"></sup>will share the inheritance as one of the brothers.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16877D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16877D\"></sup>The crucible is for silver, and the furnace is for gold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16877E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16877E\"></sup>and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> tests hearts.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>An evildoer listens to wicked lips,and a liar gives ear to a mischievous tongue.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Whoever mocks the poor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16879F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16879F\"></sup>insults his Maker;he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16879G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16879G\"></sup>glad at calamity will not go <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16879H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16879H\"></sup>unpunished.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16880I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16880I\"></sup>Grandchildren are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16880J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16880J\"></sup>the crown of the aged,and the glory of children is their fathers.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Fine speech is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16881K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16881K\"></sup>becoming to a fool;still less is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16881L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16881L\"></sup>false speech to a prince.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16882M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16882M\"></sup>A bribe is like a magic stone in the eyes of the one who gives it;wherever he turns he prospers.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16883N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16883N\"></sup>covers an offense seeks love,but he who repeats a matter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16883O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16883O\"></sup>separates close friends.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>A rebuke goes deeper into a man of understandingthan a hundred blows into a fool.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>An evil man seeks only rebellion,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16885P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16885P\"></sup>a cruel messenger will be sent against him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Let a man meet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16886Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16886Q\"></sup>a she-bear robbed of her cubs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16886R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16886R\"></sup>rather than a fool in his folly.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16887S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16887S\"></sup>returns evil for good,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16887T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16887T\"></sup>evil will not depart from his house.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The beginning of strife is like letting out water,so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16888U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16888U\"></sup>quit before the quarrel breaks out.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16889V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16889V\"></sup>justifies the wicked and he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16889W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16889W\"></sup>condemns the righteousare both alike an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Why should a fool have money in his hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16890X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16890X\"></sup>to buy wisdomwhen he has no sense?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16891Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16891Y\"></sup>A friend loves at all times,and a brother is born for adversity.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>One who lacks sense gives a pledgeand puts up security in the presence of his neighbor.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Whoever loves transgression loves strife;he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16893Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16893Z\"></sup>makes his door high seeks destruction.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16894AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16894AA\"></sup>A man of crooked heart does not discover good,and one with a dishonest tongue falls into calamity.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16895AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16895AB\"></sup>sires a fool gets himself sorrow,and the father of a fool has no joy.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16896AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16896AC\"></sup>A joyful heart is good medicine,but a crushed spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16896AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16896AD\"></sup>dries up the bones.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The wicked accepts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16897AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16897AE\"></sup>a bribe in secretto <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16897AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16897AF\"></sup>pervert the ways of justice.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16898AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16898AG\"></sup>The discerning sets his face toward wisdom,but the eyes of a fool are on the ends of the earth.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16899AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16899AH\"></sup>A foolish son is a grief to his father<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16899AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16899AI\"></sup>and bitterness to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16899AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16899AJ\"></sup>her who bore him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16900AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16900AK\"></sup>To impose a fine on a righteous man is not good,nor to strike the noble for their uprightness.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16901AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16901AL\"></sup>restrains his words has knowledge,and he who has a cool spirit is a man of understanding.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Even a fool <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16902AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16902AM\"></sup>who keeps silent is considered wise;when he closes his lips, he is deemed intelligent."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16903A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16903A\"></sup>isolates himself seeks his own desire;he breaks out against all sound judgment.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A fool takes no pleasure in understanding,but only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16904B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16904B\"></sup>in expressing his opinion.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When wickedness comes, contempt comes also,and with dishonor comes disgrace.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The words of a man's mouth are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16906C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16906C\"></sup>deep waters;the fountain of wisdom is a bubbling brook.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>It is not good to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16907D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16907D\"></sup>be partial to the wickedor to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16907E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16907E\"></sup>deprive the righteous of justice.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A fool's lips walk into a fight,and his mouth invites <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16908F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16908F\"></sup>a beating.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16909G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16909G\"></sup>A fool's mouth is his ruin,and his lips are a snare to his soul.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16910H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16910H\"></sup>The words of a whisperer are like delicious morsels;they go down into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16910I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16910I\"></sup>the inner parts of the body.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Whoever is slack in his workis a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16911J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16911J\"></sup>brother to him who destroys.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16912K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16912K\"></sup>The name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16912L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16912L\"></sup>a strong tower;the righteous man runs into it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16912M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16912M\"></sup>is safe.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16913N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16913N\"></sup>A rich man's wealth is his strong city,and like a high wall in his imagination.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16914O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16914O\"></sup>Before destruction a man's heart is haughty,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16914P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16914P\"></sup>humility comes before honor.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If one gives an answer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16915Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16915Q\"></sup>before he hears,it is his folly and shame.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>A man's spirit will endure sickness,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16916R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16916R\"></sup>a crushed spirit who can bear?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>An intelligent heart acquires knowledge,and the ear of the wise seeks knowledge.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A man's <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16918S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16918S\"></sup>gift makes room for himand brings him before the great.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The one who states his case first seems right,until the other comes and examines him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16920T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16920T\"></sup>The lot puts an end to quarrelsand decides between powerful contenders.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>A brother offended is more unyielding than a strong city,and quarreling is like the bars of a castle.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16922U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16922U\"></sup>From the fruit of a man's mouth his stomach is satisfied;he is satisfied by the yield of his lips.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16923V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16923V\"></sup>Death and life are in the power of the tongue,and those who love it will eat its fruits.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>He who finds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16924W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16924W\"></sup>a wife finds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16924X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16924X\"></sup>a good thingand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16924Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16924Y\"></sup>obtains favor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16924Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16924Z\"></sup>from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The poor use entreaties,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16925AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16925AA\"></sup>the rich answer roughly.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>A man of many companions may come to ruin,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16926AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16926AB\"></sup>there is a friend who sticks closer than a brother."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16927A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16927A\"></sup>Better is a poor person who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16927B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16927B\"></sup>walks in his integritythan one who is crooked in speech and is a fool.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Desire without knowledge is not good,and whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16928C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16928C\"></sup>makes haste with his feet misses his way.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When a man's folly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16929D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16929D\"></sup>brings his way to ruin,his heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16929E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16929E\"></sup>rages against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16930F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16930F\"></sup>Wealth brings many new friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16930G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16930G\"></sup>but a poor man is deserted by his friend.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16931H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16931H\"></sup>A false witness will not go unpunished,and he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16931I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16931I\"></sup>breathes out lies will not escape.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Many seek the favor of a generous man,and everyone is a friend to a man who gives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16932J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16932J\"></sup>gifts.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16933K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16933K\"></sup>All a poor man's brothers hate him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16933L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16933L\"></sup>how much more do his friends go far from him!He pursues them with words, but does not have them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16934M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16934M\"></sup>Whoever gets sense loves his own soul;he who keeps understanding will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16934N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16934N\"></sup>discover good.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16935O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16935O\"></sup>A false witness will not go unpunished,and he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16935P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16935P\"></sup>breathes out lies will perish.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16936Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16936Q\"></sup>It is not fitting for a fool to live in luxury,much less for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16936R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16936R\"></sup>a slave to rule over princes.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16937S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16937S\"></sup>Good sense makes one slow to anger,and it is his glory to overlook an offense.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>A king's wrath is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16938T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16938T\"></sup>the growling of a lion,but his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16938U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16938U\"></sup>favor is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16938V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16938V\"></sup>dew on the grass.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16939W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16939W\"></sup>A foolish son is ruin to his father,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16939X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16939X\"></sup>a wife's quarreling is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16939Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16939Y\"></sup>a continual dripping of rain.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16940Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16940Z\"></sup>House and wealth are inherited from fathers,but a prudent wife is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16940AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16940AA\"></sup>from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16941AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16941AB\"></sup>Slothfulness casts into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16941AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16941AC\"></sup>a deep sleep,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16941AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16941AD\"></sup>an idle person will suffer hunger.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16942AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16942AE\"></sup>keeps the commandment keeps his life;he who despises his ways will die.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16943AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16943AF\"></sup>Whoever is generous to the poor lends to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16943AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16943AG\"></sup>will repay him for his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16943AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16943AH\"></sup>deed.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16944AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16944AI\"></sup>Discipline your son, for there is hope;do not set your heart on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16944AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16944AJ\"></sup>putting him to death.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>A man of great wrath will pay the penalty,for if you deliver him, you will only have to do it again.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Listen to advice and accept instruction,that you may gain wisdom in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16946AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16946AK\"></sup>the future.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16947AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16947AL\"></sup>Many are the plans in the mind of a man,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16947AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16947AM\"></sup>it is the purpose of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16947AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16947AN\"></sup>that will stand.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>What is desired in a man is steadfast love,and a poor man is better than a liar.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16949AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16949AO\"></sup>leads to life,and whoever has it rests <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16949AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16949AP\"></sup>satisfied;he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16949AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16949AQ\"></sup>not be visited by harm.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16950AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16950AR\"></sup>The sluggard buries his hand in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16950AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16950AS\"></sup>the dishand will not even bring it back to his mouth.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16951AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16951AT\"></sup>Strike <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16951AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16951AU\"></sup>a scoffer, and the simple will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16951AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16951AV\"></sup>learn prudence;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16951AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16951AW\"></sup>reprove a man of understanding, and he will gain knowledge.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He who does violence to his father and chases away his motheris <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16952AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16952AX\"></sup>a son who brings shame and reproach.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Cease to hear instruction, my son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16953AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16953AY\"></sup>and you will stray from the words of knowledge.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A worthless witness mocks at justice,and the mouth of the wicked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16954AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16954AZ\"></sup>devours iniquity.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Condemnation is ready for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16955BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16955BA\"></sup>scoffers,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16955BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16955BB\"></sup>beating for the backs of fools."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16956A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16956A\"></sup>Wine is a mocker, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16956B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16956B\"></sup>strong drink a brawler,and whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16956C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16956C\"></sup>is led astray by it is not wise.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The terror of a king is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16957D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16957D\"></sup>the growling of a lion;whoever provokes him to anger <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16957E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16957E\"></sup>forfeits his life.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>It is an honor for a man to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16958F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16958F\"></sup>keep aloof from strife,but every fool will be quarreling.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16959G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16959G\"></sup>The sluggard does not plow in the autumn;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16959H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16959H\"></sup>he will seek at harvest and have nothing.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The purpose in a man's heart is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16960I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16960I\"></sup>deep water,but a man of understanding will draw it out.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Many a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16961J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16961J\"></sup>proclaims his own steadfast love,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16961K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16961K\"></sup>a faithful man who can find?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The righteous who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16962L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16962L\"></sup>walks in his integrity—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16962M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16962M\"></sup>blessed are his children after him!",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16963N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16963N\"></sup>A king who sits on the throne of judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16963O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16963O\"></sup>winnows all evil with his eyes.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16964P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16964P\"></sup>Who can say, “I have made my heart pure;I am clean from my sin”?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16965Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16965Q\"></sup>Unequal weights and unequal measuresare both alike an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Even a child <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16966R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16966R\"></sup>makes himself known by his acts,by whether his conduct is pure and upright.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16967S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16967S\"></sup>The hearing ear and the seeing eye,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16967T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16967T\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has made them both.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16968U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16968U\"></sup>Love not sleep, lest you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16968V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16968V\"></sup>come to poverty;open your eyes, and you will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16968W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16968W\"></sup>plenty of bread.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Bad, bad,” says the buyer,but when he goes away, then he boasts.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>There is gold and abundance of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16970X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16970X\"></sup>costly stones,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16970Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16970Y\"></sup>but the lips of knowledge are a precious jewel.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16971Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16971Z\"></sup>Take a man's garment when he has put up security for a stranger,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16971AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16971AA\"></sup>hold it in pledge when he puts up security for foreigners.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16972AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16972AB\"></sup>Bread gained by deceit is sweet to a man,but afterward his mouth will be full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16972AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16972AC\"></sup>gravel.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16973AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16973AD\"></sup>Plans are established by counsel;by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16973AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16973AE\"></sup>wise guidance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16973AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16973AF\"></sup>wage war.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16974AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16974AG\"></sup>goes about slandering reveals secrets;therefore do not associate with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16974AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16974AH\"></sup>a simple babbler.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16975AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16975AI\"></sup>If one curses his father or his mother,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16975AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16975AJ\"></sup>his lamp will be put out in utter darkness.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16976AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16976AK\"></sup>An inheritance gained hastily in the beginningwill not be blessed in the end.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Do not say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16977AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16977AL\"></sup>“I will repay evil”;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16977AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16977AM\"></sup>wait for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and he will deliver you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16978AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16978AN\"></sup>Unequal weights are an abomination to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16978AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16978AO\"></sup>false scales are not good.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>A man's <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16979AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16979AP\"></sup>steps are from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;how then can man understand his way?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>It is a snare to say rashly, “It is holy,”and to reflect only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16980AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16980AQ\"></sup>after making vows.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>A wise king <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16981AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16981AR\"></sup>winnows the wickedand drives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16981AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16981AS\"></sup>the wheel over them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16982AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16982AT\"></sup>The spirit of man is the lamp of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16982AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16982AU\"></sup>searching all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16982AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16982AV\"></sup>his innermost parts.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16983AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16983AW\"></sup>Steadfast love and faithfulness preserve the king,and by steadfast love his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16983AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16983AX\"></sup>throne is upheld.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The glory of young men is their strength,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16984AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16984AY\"></sup>the splendor of old men is their gray hair.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16985AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16985AZ\"></sup>Blows that wound cleanse away evil;strokes make clean <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16985BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16985BA\"></sup>the innermost parts."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>The king's heart is a stream of water in the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16986A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16986A\"></sup>turns it wherever he will.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16987B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16987B\"></sup>Every way of a man is right in his own eyes,but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16987C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16987C\"></sup>weighs the heart.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16988D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16988D\"></sup>To do righteousness and justiceis more acceptable to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> than sacrifice.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16989E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16989E\"></sup>Haughty eyes and a proud heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16989F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16989F\"></sup>the lamp of the wicked, are sin.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The plans of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16990G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16990G\"></sup>the diligent lead surely to abundance,but everyone who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16990H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16990H\"></sup>hasty comes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16990I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16990I\"></sup>only to poverty.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16991J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16991J\"></sup>The getting of treasures by a lying tongueis a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16991K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16991K\"></sup>fleeting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16991L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16991L\"></sup>vapor and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16991M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16991M\"></sup>snare of death.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The violence of the wicked will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16992N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16992N\"></sup>sweep them away,because they refuse to do what is just.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The way of the guilty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16993O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16993O\"></sup>is crooked,but the conduct of the pure is upright.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16994P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16994P\"></sup>better to live in a corner of the housetopthan in a house shared with a quarrelsome wife.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The soul of the wicked desires evil;his neighbor finds no mercy in his eyes.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16996Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16996Q\"></sup>a scoffer is punished, the simple becomes wise;when a wise man is instructed, he gains knowledge.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The Righteous One <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16997R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16997R\"></sup>observes the house of the wicked;he throws the wicked down to ruin.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16998S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16998S\"></sup>Whoever closes his ear to the cry of the poorwill himself call out and not be answered.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16999T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16999T\"></sup>A gift in secret averts anger,and a concealed bribe, strong wrath.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When justice is done, it is a joy to the righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17000U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17000U\"></sup>but terror to evildoers.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>One who wanders from the way of good sense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17001V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17001V\"></sup>will rest in the assembly of the dead.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Whoever loves pleasure will be a poor man;he who loves wine and oil will not be rich.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17003W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17003W\"></sup>The wicked is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17003X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17003X\"></sup>ransom for the righteous,and the traitor for the upright.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17004Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17004Y\"></sup>better to live in a desert landthan with a quarrelsome and fretful woman.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17005Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17005Z\"></sup>Precious treasure and oil are in a wise man's dwelling,but a foolish man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17005AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17005AA\"></sup>devours it.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17006AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17006AB\"></sup>pursues righteousness and kindnesswill find <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17006AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17006AC\"></sup>life, righteousness, and honor.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17007AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17007AD\"></sup>A wise man scales the city of the mightyand brings down the stronghold in which they trust.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17008AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17008AE\"></sup>Whoever keeps his mouth and his tongue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17008AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17008AF\"></sup>keeps himself out of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17008AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17008AG\"></sup>trouble.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17009AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17009AH\"></sup>“Scoffer” is the name of the arrogant, haughty manwho acts with arrogant pride.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The desire of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17010AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17010AI\"></sup>the sluggard kills him,for his hands refuse to labor.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>All day long he craves and craves,but the righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17011AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17011AJ\"></sup>gives and does not hold back.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17012AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17012AK\"></sup>The sacrifice of the wicked is an abomination;how much more <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17012AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17012AL\"></sup>when he brings it with evil intent.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17013AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17013AM\"></sup>A false witness will perish,but the word of a man who hears will endure.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>A wicked man puts on a bold face,but the upright <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17014AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17014AN\"></sup>gives thought to his ways.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17015AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17015AO\"></sup>No wisdom, no understanding, no counselcan avail against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17016AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17016AP\"></sup>The horse is made ready for the day of battle,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17016AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17016AQ\"></sup>the victory belongs to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17017A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17017A\"></sup>A good name is to be chosen rather than great riches,and favor is better than silver or gold.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17018B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17018B\"></sup>The rich and the poor meet together;the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17018C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17018C\"></sup>the Maker of them all.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17019D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17019D\"></sup>The prudent sees danger and hides himself,but the simple go on and suffer for it.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The reward for humility and fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17020E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17020E\"></sup>riches and honor and life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17021F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17021F\"></sup>Thorns and snares are in the way of the crooked;whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17021G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17021G\"></sup>guards his soul will keep far from them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17022H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17022H\"></sup>Train up a child in the way he should go;even when he is old he will not depart from it.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17023I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17023I\"></sup>The rich rules over the poor,and the borrower is the slave of the lender.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17024J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17024J\"></sup>sows injustice will reap calamity,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17024K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17024K\"></sup>the rod of his fury will fail.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17025L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17025L\"></sup>Whoever has a bountiful eye will be blessed,for he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17025M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17025M\"></sup>shares his bread with the poor.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17026N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17026N\"></sup>Drive out a scoffer, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17026O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17026O\"></sup>and strife will go out,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17026P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17026P\"></sup>quarreling and abuse will cease.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17027Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17027Q\"></sup>loves purity of heart,and whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17027R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17027R\"></sup>speech is gracious, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17027S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17027S\"></sup>will have the king as his friend.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> keep watch over knowledge,but he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17028T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17028T\"></sup>overthrows the words of the traitor.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17029U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17029U\"></sup>The sluggard says, “There is a lion outside!I shall be killed in the streets!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The mouth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17030V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17030V\"></sup>forbidden women is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17030W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17030W\"></sup>a deep pit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17030X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17030X\"></sup>he with whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is angry will fall into it.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Folly is bound up in the heart of a child,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17031Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17031Y\"></sup>the rod of discipline drives it far from him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Whoever oppresses the poor to increase his own wealth,or gives to the rich, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17032Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17032Z\"></sup>will only come to poverty.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17033AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17033AA\"></sup>Incline your ear, and hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17033AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17033AB\"></sup>the words of the wise,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17033AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17033AC\"></sup>and apply your heart to my knowledge,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>for it will be pleasant if you keep them within you,if all of them are ready on your lips.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>That your trust may be in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,I have made them known to you today, even to you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Have I not written for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17036AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17036AD\"></sup>thirty sayingsof counsel and knowledge,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17037AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17037AE\"></sup>make you know what is right and true,that you may give a true answer to those who sent you?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17038AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17038AF\"></sup>Do not rob the poor, because he is poor,or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17038AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17038AG\"></sup>crush the afflicted at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17038AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17038AH\"></sup>the gate,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17039AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17039AI\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will plead their causeand rob of life those who rob them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Make no friendship with a man given to anger,nor go with a wrathful man,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>lest you learn his waysand entangle yourself in a snare.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Be not one of those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17042AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17042AJ\"></sup>give pledges,who put up security for debts.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>If you have nothing with which to pay,why should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17043AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17043AK\"></sup>your bed be taken from under you?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Do not move the ancient <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17044AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17044AL\"></sup>landmarkthat your fathers have set.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Do you see a man skillful in his work?He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17045AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17045AM\"></sup>stand before kings;he will not stand before obscure men."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>When you sit down to eat with a ruler,observe carefully what is before you,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and put a knife to your throatif you are given to appetite.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17048A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17048A\"></sup>Do not desire his delicacies,for they are deceptive food.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17049B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17049B\"></sup>Do not toil to acquire wealth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17049C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17049C\"></sup>be discerning enough to desist.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When your eyes light on it, it is gone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17050D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17050D\"></sup>for suddenly it sprouts wings,flying like an eagle toward heaven.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17051E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17051E\"></sup>Do not eat the bread of a man who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17051F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17051F\"></sup>stingy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17051G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17051G\"></sup>do not desire his delicacies,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>for he is like one who is inwardly calculating.“Eat and drink!” he says to you,but his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17052H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17052H\"></sup>heart is not with you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You will vomit up the morsels that you have eaten,and waste your pleasant words.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do not speak in the hearing of a fool,for he will despise the good sense of your words.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17055I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17055I\"></sup>Do not move an ancient landmarkor enter the fields of the fatherless,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>for their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17056J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17056J\"></sup>Redeemer is strong;he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17056K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17056K\"></sup>plead their cause against you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Apply your heart to instructionand your ear to words of knowledge.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Do not withhold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17058L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17058L\"></sup>discipline from a child;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17058M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17058M\"></sup>if you strike him with a rod, he will not die.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If you strike him with the rod,you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17059N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17059N\"></sup>save his soul from Sheol.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17060O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17060O\"></sup>My son, if your heart is wise,my heart too will be glad.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17061P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17061P\"></sup>inmost being will exultwhen your lips speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17061Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17061Q\"></sup>what is right.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Let not your heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17062R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17062R\"></sup>envy sinners,but continue in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17062S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17062S\"></sup>the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> all the day.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17063T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17063T\"></sup>there is a future,and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17063U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17063U\"></sup>hope will not be cut off.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Hear, my son, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17064V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17064V\"></sup>be wise,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17064W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17064W\"></sup>direct your heart in the way.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Be not among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17065X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17065X\"></sup>drunkardsor among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17065Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17065Y\"></sup>gluttonous eaters of meat,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>for the drunkard and the glutton will come to poverty,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17066Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17066Z\"></sup>slumber will clothe them with rags.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17067AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17067AA\"></sup>Listen to your father who gave you life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17067AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17067AB\"></sup>and do not despise your mother when she is old.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17068AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17068AC\"></sup>Buy truth, and do not sell it;buy wisdom, instruction, and understanding.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17069AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17069AD\"></sup>The father of the righteous will greatly rejoice;he who fathers a wise son will be glad in him.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17070AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17070AE\"></sup>Let your father and mother be glad;let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17070AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17070AF\"></sup>her who bore you rejoice.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>My son, give me your heart,and let your eyes observe my ways.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For a prostitute is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17072AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17072AG\"></sup>a deep pit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17072AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17072AH\"></sup>an adulteress is a narrow <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17072AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17072AI\"></sup>well.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17073AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17073AJ\"></sup>She lies in wait like a robberand increases the traitors among mankind.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17074AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17074AK\"></sup>Who has woe? Who has sorrow?Who has strife? Who has complaining?Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17074AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17074AL\"></sup>wounds without cause?Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17074AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17074AM\"></sup>redness of eyes?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17075AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17075AN\"></sup>tarry long over wine;those who go to try <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17075AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17075AO\"></sup>mixed wine.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Do not look at wine when it is red,when it sparkles in the cupand goes down smoothly.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>In the end it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17077AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17077AP\"></sup>bites like a serpentand stings like an adder.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Your eyes will see strange things,and your heart utter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17078AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17078AQ\"></sup>perverse things.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>You will be like one who lies down in the midst of the sea,like one who lies on the top of a mast.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17080AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17080AR\"></sup>struck me,” you will say, “but I was not hurt;they beat me, but I did not feel it.When shall I awake?I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17080AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17080AS\"></sup>must have another drink.”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>Be not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17081A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17081A\"></sup>envious of evil men,nor desire to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17081B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17081B\"></sup>with them,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for their hearts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17082C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17082C\"></sup>devise violence,and their lips <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17082D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17082D\"></sup>talk of trouble.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>By <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17083E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17083E\"></sup>wisdom a house is built,and by understanding it is established;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>by knowledge the rooms are filledwith all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17084F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17084F\"></sup>precious and pleasant riches.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17085G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17085G\"></sup>A wise man is full of strength,and a man of knowledge enhances his might,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>for by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17086H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17086H\"></sup>wise guidance you can wage your war,and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17086I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17086I\"></sup>abundance of counselors there is victory.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Wisdom is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17087J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17087J\"></sup>too high for a fool;in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17087K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17087K\"></sup>the gate he does not open his mouth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17088L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17088L\"></sup>plans to do evilwill be called a schemer.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17089M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17089M\"></sup>The devising of folly is sin,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17089N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17089N\"></sup>the scoffer is an abomination to mankind.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>If you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17090O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17090O\"></sup>faint in the day of adversity,your strength is small.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17091P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17091P\"></sup>Rescue those who are being taken away to death;hold back those who are stumbling to the slaughter.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If you say, “Behold, we did not know this,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17092Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17092Q\"></sup>does not he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17092R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17092R\"></sup>weighs the heart perceive it?Does not he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17092S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17092S\"></sup>keeps watch over your soul know it,and will he not repay man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17092T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17092T\"></sup>according to his work?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17093U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17093U\"></sup>eat honey, for it is good,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17093V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17093V\"></sup>the drippings of the honeycomb are sweet to your taste.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Know that wisdom is such to your soul;if you find it, there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17094W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17094W\"></sup>a future,and your hope will not be cut off.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17095X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17095X\"></sup>Lie not in wait as a wicked man against the dwelling of the righteous;do no violence to his home;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17096Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17096Y\"></sup>for the righteous falls <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17096Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17096Z\"></sup>seven times and rises again,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17096AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17096AA\"></sup>the wicked stumble in times of calamity.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17097AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17097AB\"></sup>Do not rejoice when your enemy falls,and let not your heart be glad when he stumbles,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>lest the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> see it and be displeased,and turn away his anger from him.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17099AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17099AC\"></sup>Fret not yourself because of evildoers,and be not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17099AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17099AD\"></sup>envious of the wicked,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>for the evil man has no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17100AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17100AE\"></sup>future;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17100AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17100AF\"></sup>the lamp of the wicked will be put out.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>My son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17101AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17101AG\"></sup>fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and the king,and do not join with those who do otherwise,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>for disaster will arise suddenly from them,and who knows the ruin that will come from them both?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>These also are sayings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17103AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17103AH\"></sup>the wise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17103AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17103AI\"></sup>Partiality in judging is not good.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17104AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17104AJ\"></sup>says to the wicked, “You are in the right,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17104AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17104AK\"></sup>will be cursed by peoples, abhorred by nations,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>but those who rebuke the wicked will have delight,and a good blessing will come upon them.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Whoever gives an honest answerkisses the lips.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17107AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17107AL\"></sup>Prepare your work outside;get everything ready for yourself in the field,and after that build your house.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17108AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17108AM\"></sup>Be not a witness against your neighbor without cause,and do not deceive with your lips.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Do not say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17109AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17109AN\"></sup>“I will do to him as he has done to me;I will pay the man back for what he has done.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17110AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17110AO\"></sup>I passed by the field of a sluggard,by the vineyard of a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17110AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17110AP\"></sup>lacking sense,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>and behold, it was all overgrown with thorns;the ground was covered with nettles,and its stone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17111AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17111AQ\"></sup>wall was broken down.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Then I saw and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17112AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17112AR\"></sup>considered it;I looked and received instruction.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17113AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17113AS\"></sup>A little sleep, a little slumber,a little folding of the hands to rest,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>and poverty will come upon you like a robber,and want like an armed man."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>These also are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17115A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17115A\"></sup>proverbs of Solomon which the men of Hezekiah king of Judah copied.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>It is the glory of God to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17116B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17116B\"></sup>conceal things,but the glory of kings is to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17116C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17116C\"></sup>search things out.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>As the heavens for height, and the earth for depth,so the heart of kings is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17117D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17117D\"></sup>unsearchable.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Take away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17118E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17118E\"></sup>the dross from the silver,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17118F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17118F\"></sup>the smith has material for a vessel;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>take away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17119G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17119G\"></sup>the wicked from the presence of the king,and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17119H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17119H\"></sup>throne will be established in righteousness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not put yourself forward in the king's presenceor stand in the place of the great,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17121I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17121I\"></sup>it is better to be told, “Come up here,”than to be put lower in the presence of a noble.What your eyes have seen",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17122J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17122J\"></sup>do not hastily bring into court,for what will you do in the end,when your neighbor puts you to shame?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17123K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17123K\"></sup>Argue your case with your neighbor himself,and do not reveal another's secret,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>lest he who hears you bring shame upon you,and your ill repute have no end.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17125L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17125L\"></sup>A word fitly spokenis like apples of gold in a setting of silver.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17126M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17126M\"></sup>a gold ring or an ornament of goldis a wise reprover to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17126N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17126N\"></sup>a listening ear.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Like the cold of snow in the time of harvestis <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17127O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17127O\"></sup>a faithful messenger to those who send him;he refreshes the soul of his masters.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17128P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17128P\"></sup>clouds and wind without rainis a man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17128Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17128Q\"></sup>boasts of a gift he does not give.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>With <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17129R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17129R\"></sup>patience a ruler may be persuaded,and a soft tongue will break a bone.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17130S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17130S\"></sup>found honey, eat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17130T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17130T\"></sup>only enough for you,lest you have your fill of it and vomit it.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Let your foot be seldom in your neighbor's house,lest he have his fill of you and hate you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>A man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17132U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17132U\"></sup>bears false witness against his neighboris like a war club, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17132V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17132V\"></sup>a sword, or a sharp arrow.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Trusting in a treacherous man in time of troubleis like a bad tooth or a foot that slips.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17134W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17134W\"></sup>sings songs to a heavy heartis like one who takes off a garment on a cold day,and like vinegar on soda.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17135X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17135X\"></sup>If your enemy is hungry, give him bread to eat,and if he is thirsty, give him water to drink,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>for you will heap <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17136Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17136Y\"></sup>burning coals on his head,and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will reward you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The north wind brings forth rain,and a backbiting tongue, angry looks.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17138Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17138Z\"></sup>It is better to live in a corner of the housetopthan in a house shared with a quarrelsome wife.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Like cold water to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17139AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17139AA\"></sup>a thirsty soul,so is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17139AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17139AB\"></sup>good news from a far country.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17140AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17140AC\"></sup>a muddied spring or a polluted fountainis a righteous man who gives way before the wicked.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17141AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17141AD\"></sup>not good to eat much honey,nor is it glorious to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17141AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17141AE\"></sup>seek one's own glory.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17142AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17142AF\"></sup>without self-controlis like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17142AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17142AG\"></sup>a city broken into and left without walls."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>Like snow in summer or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17143A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17143A\"></sup>rain in harvest,so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17143B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17143B\"></sup>honor is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17143C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17143C\"></sup>not fitting for a fool.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17144D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17144D\"></sup>a sparrow in its flitting, like a swallow in its flying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17144E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17144E\"></sup>a curse that is causeless does not alight.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17145F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17145F\"></sup>A whip for the horse, a bridle for the donkey,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17145G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17145G\"></sup>a rod for the back of fools.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17146H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17146H\"></sup>Answer not a fool according to his folly,lest you be like him yourself.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17147I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17147I\"></sup>Answer a fool according to his folly,lest he be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17147J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17147J\"></sup>wise in his own eyes.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Whoever sends a message by the hand of a foolcuts off his own feet and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17148K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17148K\"></sup>drinks violence.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Like a lame man's legs, which hang useless,is a proverb in the mouth of fools.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Like one who binds the stone in the slingis <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17150L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17150L\"></sup>one who gives honor to a fool.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17151M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17151M\"></sup>a thorn that goes up into the hand of a drunkardis a proverb in the mouth of fools.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Like an archer who wounds everyoneis one who hires a passing fool or drunkard.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17153N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17153N\"></sup>a dog that returns to his vomitis <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17153O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17153O\"></sup>a fool who repeats his folly.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Do you see a man who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17154P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17154P\"></sup>wise in his own eyes?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17154Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17154Q\"></sup>There is more hope for a fool than for him.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17155R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17155R\"></sup>The sluggard says, “There is a lion in the road!There is a lion in the streets!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As a door turns on its hinges,so does a sluggard on his bed.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17157S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17157S\"></sup>The sluggard buries his hand in the dish;it wears him out to bring it back to his mouth.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The sluggard is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17158T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17158T\"></sup>wiser in his own eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17158U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17158U\"></sup>than seven men who can answer sensibly.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Whoever meddles in a quarrel not his ownis like one who takes a passing dog by the ears.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Like a madman who throws <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17160V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17160V\"></sup>firebrands, arrows, and death",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>is the man who deceives his neighborand says, “I am only joking!”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For lack of wood the fire goes out,and where there is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17162W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17162W\"></sup>whisperer, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17162X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17162X\"></sup>quarreling ceases.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>As charcoal to hot embers and wood to fire,so is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17163Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17163Y\"></sup>a quarrelsome man for kindling strife.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17164Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17164Z\"></sup>The words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17164AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17164AA\"></sup>a whisperer are like delicious morsels;they go down into the inner parts of the body.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17165AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17165AB\"></sup>Like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17165AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17165AC\"></sup>glaze covering an earthen vesselare fervent lips with an evil heart.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Whoever hates disguises himself with his lipsand harbors deceit in his heart;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17167AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17167AD\"></sup>when he speaks graciously, believe him not,for there are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17167AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17167AE\"></sup>seven abominations in his heart;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>though his hatred be covered with deception,his wickedness will be exposed in the assembly.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17169AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17169AF\"></sup>Whoever digs a pit will fall into it,and a stone will come back on him who starts it rolling.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A lying tongue hates its victims,and a flattering mouth works ruin."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>Do not boast about tomorrow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17171A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17171A\"></sup>for you do not know what a day may bring.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17172B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17172B\"></sup>another praise you, and not your own mouth;a stranger, and not your own lips.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A stone is heavy, and sand is weighty,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17173C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17173C\"></sup>a fool's provocation is heavier than both.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Wrath is cruel, anger is overwhelming,but who can stand before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17174D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17174D\"></sup>jealousy?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17175E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17175E\"></sup>Better is open rebukethan hidden love.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Faithful are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17176F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17176F\"></sup>the wounds of a friend;profuse are the kisses of an enemy.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>One who is full loathes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17177G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17177G\"></sup>honey,but to one who is hungry everything bitter is sweet.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17178H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17178H\"></sup>a bird that strays from its nestis a man who strays from his home.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17179I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17179I\"></sup>Oil and perfume make the heart glad,and the sweetness of a friend comes from his earnest counsel.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not forsake your friend and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17180J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17180J\"></sup>your father's friend,and do not go to your brother's house in the day of your calamity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17180K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17180K\"></sup>Better is a neighbor who is nearthan a brother who is far away.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17181L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17181L\"></sup>Be wise, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17181M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17181M\"></sup>my son, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17181N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17181N\"></sup>make my heart glad,that I may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17181O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17181O\"></sup>answer him who reproaches me.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17182P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17182P\"></sup>The prudent sees danger and hides himself,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17182Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17182Q\"></sup>the simple go on and suffer for it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17183R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17183R\"></sup>Take a man's garment when he has put up security for a stranger,and hold it in pledge when he puts up security for an adulteress.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Whoever blesses his neighbor with a loud voice,rising early in the morning,will be counted as cursing.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17185S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17185S\"></sup>A continual dripping on a rainy dayand a quarrelsome wife are alike;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>to restrain her is to restrain the windor to grasp oil in one's right hand.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Iron sharpens iron,and one man sharpens another.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17188T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17188T\"></sup>Whoever tends a fig tree will eat its fruit,and he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17188U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17188U\"></sup>guards his master will be honored.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>As in water face reflects face,so the heart of man reflects the man.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17190V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17190V\"></sup>Sheol and Abaddon are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17190W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17190W\"></sup>never satisfied,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17190X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17190X\"></sup>never satisfied are the eyes of man.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17191Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17191Y\"></sup>The crucible is for silver, and the furnace is for gold,and a man is tested by his praise.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17192Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17192Z\"></sup>Crush a fool in a mortar with a pestlealong with crushed grain,yet his folly will not depart from him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17193AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17193AA\"></sup>Know well the condition of your flocks,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17193AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17193AB\"></sup>give attention to your herds,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17194AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17194AC\"></sup>riches do not last forever;and does a crown endure to all generations?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17195AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17195AD\"></sup>When the grass is gone and the new growth appearsand the vegetation of the mountains is gathered,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17196AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17196AE\"></sup>the lambs will provide your clothing,and the goats the price of a field.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17197AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17197AF\"></sup>There will be enough goats' milk for your food,for the food of your householdand maintenance for your girls."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17198A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17198A\"></sup>The wicked flee when no one pursues,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17198B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17198B\"></sup>the righteous are bold as a lion.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When a land transgresses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17199C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17199C\"></sup>it has many rulers,but with a man of understanding and knowledge,its stability will long continue.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17200D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17200D\"></sup>A poor man who oppresses the pooris a beating rain that leaves no food.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Those who forsake the law <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17201E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17201E\"></sup>praise the wicked,but those who keep the law <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17201F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17201F\"></sup>strive against them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Evil men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17202G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17202G\"></sup>do not understand justice,but those who seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17202H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17202H\"></sup>understand it completely.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17203I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17203I\"></sup>Better is a poor man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17203J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17203J\"></sup>walks in his integritythan a rich man who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17203K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17203K\"></sup>crooked in his ways.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The one who keeps the law is a son with understanding,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17204L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17204L\"></sup>a companion of gluttons shames his father.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Whoever multiplies his wealth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17205M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17205M\"></sup>by interest and profit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17205N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17205N\"></sup>gathers it for him who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17205O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17205O\"></sup>generous to the poor.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If one turns away his ear from hearing the law,even his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17206P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17206P\"></sup>prayer is an abomination.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Whoever misleads the upright into an evil way<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17207Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17207Q\"></sup>will fall into his own pit,but the blameless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17207R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17207R\"></sup>will have a goodly inheritance.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>A rich man is wise in his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17208S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17208S\"></sup>own eyes,but a poor man who has understanding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17208T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17208T\"></sup>will find him out.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17209U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17209U\"></sup>the righteous triumph, there is great glory,but when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17209V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17209V\"></sup>the wicked rise, people hide themselves.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17210W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17210W\"></sup>conceals his transgressions will not prosper,but he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17210X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17210X\"></sup>confesses and forsakes them will obtain mercy.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Blessed is the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17211Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17211Y\"></sup>fears the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> always,but whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17211Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17211Z\"></sup>hardens his heart will fall into calamity.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17212AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17212AA\"></sup>a roaring lion or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17212AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17212AB\"></sup>a charging bearis <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17212AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17212AC\"></sup>a wicked ruler over a poor people.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>A ruler who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17213AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17213AD\"></sup>lacks understanding is a cruel oppressor,but he who hates unjust gain will prolong his days.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If one is burdened with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17214AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17214AE\"></sup>the blood of another,he will be a fugitive until death;let no one help him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17215AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17215AF\"></sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17215AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17215AG\"></sup>walks in integrity will be delivered,but he who is crooked in his ways will suddenly fall.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17216AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17216AH\"></sup>Whoever works his land will have plenty of bread,but he who follows worthless pursuits will have plenty of poverty.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>A faithful man will abound with blessings,but whoever hastens to be rich <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17217AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17217AI\"></sup>will not go unpunished.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To show <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17218AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17218AJ\"></sup>partiality is not good,but for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17218AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17218AK\"></sup>a piece of bread a man will do wrong.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17219AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17219AL\"></sup>stingy man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17219AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17219AM\"></sup>hastens after wealthand does not know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17219AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17219AN\"></sup>poverty will come upon him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17220AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17220AO\"></sup>rebukes a man will afterward find more favorthan <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17220AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17220AP\"></sup>he who flatters with his tongue.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Whoever robs his father or his motherand says, “That is no transgression,”is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17221AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17221AQ\"></sup>a companion to a man who destroys.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>A greedy man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17222AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17222AR\"></sup>stirs up strife,but the one who trusts in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17222AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17222AS\"></sup>be enriched.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17223AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17223AT\"></sup>trusts in his own mind is a fool,but he who walks in wisdom will be delivered.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17224AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17224AU\"></sup>gives to the poor will not want,but he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17224AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17224AV\"></sup>hides his eyes will get many a curse.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17225AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17225AW\"></sup>the wicked rise, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17225AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17225AX\"></sup>people hide themselves,but when they perish, the righteous increase."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17226A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17226A\"></sup>He who is often reproved, yet stiffens his neck,will suddenly be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17226B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17226B\"></sup>broken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17226C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17226C\"></sup>beyond healing.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17227D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17227D\"></sup>the righteous increase, the people rejoice,but when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17227E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17227E\"></sup>the wicked rule, the people groan.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17228F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17228F\"></sup>loves wisdom makes his father glad,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17228G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17228G\"></sup>a companion of prostitutes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17228H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17228H\"></sup>squanders his wealth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>By justice a king <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17229I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17229I\"></sup>builds up the land,but he who exacts gifts tears it down.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17230J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17230J\"></sup>A man who flatters his neighborspreads <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17230K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17230K\"></sup>a net for his feet.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>An evil man is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17231L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17231L\"></sup>ensnared in his transgression,but a righteous man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17231M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17231M\"></sup>sings and rejoices.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>A righteous man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17232N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17232N\"></sup>knows the rights of the poor;a wicked man does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17232O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17232O\"></sup>understand such knowledge.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17233P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17233P\"></sup>Scoffers set a city aflame,but the wise turn away wrath.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If a wise man has an argument with a fool,the fool only rages and laughs, and there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17234Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17234Q\"></sup>no quiet.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Bloodthirsty men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17235R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17235R\"></sup>hate one who is blamelessand seek the life of the upright.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>A fool gives full vent to his spirit,but a wise man quietly holds it back.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If a ruler listens to falsehood,all his officials will be wicked.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The poor man and the oppressor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17238S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17238S\"></sup>meet together;the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17238T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17238T\"></sup>gives light to the eyes of both.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If a king <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17239U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17239U\"></sup>faithfully judges the poor,his throne will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17239V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17239V\"></sup>be established forever.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17240W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17240W\"></sup>The rod and reproof give wisdom,but a child left to himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17240X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17240X\"></sup>brings shame to his mother.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When the wicked increase, transgression increases,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17241Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17241Y\"></sup>the righteous will look upon their downfall.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17242Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17242Z\"></sup>Discipline your son, and he will give you rest;he will give delight to your heart.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Where <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17243AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17243AA\"></sup>there is no prophetic vision the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17243AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17243AB\"></sup>cast off restraint,but blessed is he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17243AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17243AC\"></sup>keeps the law.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>By mere words a servant is not disciplined,for though he understands, he will not respond.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Do you see a man who is hasty in his words?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17245AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17245AD\"></sup>There is more hope for a fool than for him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Whoever pampers his servant from childhoodwill in the end find him his heir.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17247AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17247AE\"></sup>A man of wrath stirs up strife,and one given to anger causes much transgression.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17248AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17248AF\"></sup>One's pride will bring him low,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17248AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17248AG\"></sup>but he who is lowly in spirit will obtain honor.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The partner of a thief <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17249AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17249AH\"></sup>hates his own life;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17249AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17249AI\"></sup>he hears the curse, but discloses nothing.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17250AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17250AJ\"></sup>The fear of man lays a snare,but whoever trusts in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is safe.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17251AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17251AK\"></sup>seek the face of a ruler,but it is from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17251AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17251AL\"></sup>gets justice.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17252AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17252AM\"></sup>An unjust man is an abomination to the righteous,but one whose way is straight is an abomination to the wicked."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>The words of Agur son of Jakeh. The oracle.The man declares, I am weary, O God;I am weary, O God, and worn out.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Surely I am too <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17254A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17254A\"></sup>stupid to be a man.I have not the understanding of a man.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I have not learned wisdom,nor have I knowledge of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17255B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17255B\"></sup>the Holy One.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17256C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17256C\"></sup>ascended to heaven and come down?Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17256D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17256D\"></sup>gathered the wind in his fists?Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17256E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17256E\"></sup>wrapped up the waters in a garment?Who has established all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17256F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17256F\"></sup>the ends of the earth?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17256G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17256G\"></sup>What is his name, and what is his son's name?Surely you know!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17257H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17257H\"></sup>Every word of God proves true;he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17257I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17257I\"></sup>a shield to those who take refuge in him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17258J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17258J\"></sup>Do not add to his words,lest he rebuke you and you be found a liar.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Two things I ask of you;deny them not to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17259K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17259K\"></sup>before I die:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Remove far from me falsehood and lying;give me neither poverty nor riches;feed me with the food that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17260L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17260L\"></sup>needful for me,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>lest I be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17261M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17261M\"></sup>full and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17261N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17261N\"></sup>deny youand say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17261O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17261O\"></sup>“Who is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?”or lest I be poor and steal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17261P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17261P\"></sup>and profane the name of my God.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17262Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17262Q\"></sup>Do not slander a servant to his master,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17262R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17262R\"></sup>lest he curse you, and you be held guilty.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>There are those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17263S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17263S\"></sup>curse their fathersand do not bless their mothers.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>There are those who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17264T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17264T\"></sup>clean in their own eyesbut are not washed of their filth.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>There are those—how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17265U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17265U\"></sup>lofty are their eyes,how high their eyelids lift!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>There are those whose teeth are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17266V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17266V\"></sup>swords,whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17266W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17266W\"></sup>fangs are knives,to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17266X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17266X\"></sup>devour the poor from off the earth,the needy from among mankind.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The leech has two daughters:Give and Give.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17267Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17267Y\"></sup>Three things are never satisfied;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17267Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17267Z\"></sup>four never say, “Enough”:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17268AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17268AA\"></sup>Sheol, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17268AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17268AB\"></sup>the barren womb,the land never satisfied with water,and the fire that never says, “Enough.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The eye that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17269AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17269AC\"></sup>mocks a fatherand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17269AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17269AD\"></sup>scorns to obey a motherwill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17269AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17269AE\"></sup>be picked out by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17269AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17269AF\"></sup>the ravens of the valleyand eaten by the vultures.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17270AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17270AG\"></sup>Three things are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17270AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17270AH\"></sup>too wonderful for me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17270AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17270AI\"></sup>four I do not understand:",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>the way of an eagle in the sky,the way of a serpent on a rock,the way of a ship on the high seas,and the way of a man with a virgin.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>This is the way of an adulteress:she eats and wipes her mouthand says, “I have done no wrong.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Under <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17273AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17273AJ\"></sup>three things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17273AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17273AK\"></sup>the earth trembles;under <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17273AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17273AL\"></sup>four it cannot bear up:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17274AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17274AM\"></sup>a slave when he becomes king,and a fool when he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17274AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17274AN\"></sup>filled with food;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17275AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17275AO\"></sup>an unloved woman when she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17275AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17275AP\"></sup>gets a husband,and a maidservant when she displaces her mistress.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17276AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17276AQ\"></sup>Four things on earth are small,but they are exceedingly wise:",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17277AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17277AR\"></sup>the ants are a people not strong,yet they provide their food in the summer;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17278AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17278AS\"></sup>the rock badgers are a people not mighty,yet they make their homes in the cliffs;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>the locusts have no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17279AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17279AT\"></sup>king,yet all of them march in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17279AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17279AU\"></sup>rank;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>the lizard you can take in your hands,yet it is in kings' palaces.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17281AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17281AV\"></sup>Three things are stately in their tread;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17281AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17281AW\"></sup>four are stately in their stride:",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>the lion, which is mightiest among beastsand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17282AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17282AX\"></sup>does not turn back before any;",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17283AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17283AY\"></sup>strutting rooster, the he-goat,and a king whose army is with him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>If you have been foolish, exalting yourself,or if you have been devising evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17284AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17284AZ\"></sup>put your hand on your mouth.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For pressing milk produces curds,pressing the nose produces blood,and pressing anger produces strife."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>The words of King Lemuel. An oracle that his mother taught him:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>What are you doing, my son? What are you doing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17287A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17287A\"></sup>son of my womb?What are you doing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17287B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17287B\"></sup>son of my vows?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17288C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17288C\"></sup>not give your strength to women,your ways to those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17288D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17288D\"></sup>who destroy kings.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17289E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17289E\"></sup>It is not for kings, O Lemuel,it is not for kings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17289F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17289F\"></sup>to drink wine,or for rulers to take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17289G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17289G\"></sup>strong drink,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>lest they drink and forget what has been decreedand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17290H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17290H\"></sup>pervert the rights of all the afflicted.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Give strong drink to the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17291I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17291I\"></sup>is perishing,and wine to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17291J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17291J\"></sup>those in bitter distress;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17292K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17292K\"></sup>let them drink and forget their povertyand remember their misery no more.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17293L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17293L\"></sup>Open your mouth for the mute,for the rights of all who are destitute.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Open your mouth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17294M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17294M\"></sup>judge righteously,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17294N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17294N\"></sup>defend the rights of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17294O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17294O\"></sup>the poor and needy.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17295P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17295P\"></sup>An excellent wife who can find?She is far more precious than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17295Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17295Q\"></sup>jewels.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The heart of her husband trusts in her,and he will have no lack of gain.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>She does him good, and not harm,all the days of her life.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17298R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17298R\"></sup>seeks wool and flax,and works with willing hands.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>She is like the ships of the merchant;she brings her food from afar.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17300S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17300S\"></sup>rises while it is yet nightand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17300T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17300T\"></sup>provides food for her householdand portions for her maidens.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>She considers a field and buys it;with the fruit of her hands she plants a vineyard.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17302U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17302U\"></sup>dresses herself with strengthand makes her arms strong.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>She perceives that her merchandise is profitable.Her lamp does not go out at night.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>She puts her hands to the distaff,and her hands hold the spindle.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17305V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17305V\"></sup>opens her hand to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17305W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17305W\"></sup>the poorand reaches out her hands to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17305X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17305X\"></sup>the needy.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>She is not afraid of snow for her household,for all her household are clothed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17306Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17306Y\"></sup>scarlet.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>She makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17307Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17307Z\"></sup>bed coverings for herself;her clothing is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17307AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17307AA\"></sup>fine linen and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17307AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17307AB\"></sup>purple.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Her husband is known in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17308AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17308AC\"></sup>the gateswhen he sits among the elders of the land.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>She makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17309AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17309AD\"></sup>linen garments and sells them;she delivers sashes to the merchant.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17310AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17310AE\"></sup>Strength and dignity are her clothing,and she laughs at the time to come.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>She opens her mouth with wisdom,and the teaching of kindness is on her tongue.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>She looks well to the ways of her householdand does not eat the bread of idleness.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Her children rise up and call her blessed;her husband also, and he praises her:",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17314AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17314AF\"></sup>women have done <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17314AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17314AG\"></sup>excellently,but you surpass them all.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-17315AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-17315AH\"></sup>Charm is deceitful, and beauty is vain,but a woman who fears the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is to be praised.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Give her of the fruit of her hands,and let her works praise her in the gates."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;